Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.54,0:08:46.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃 放再低点
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.94,0:08:48.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要起风了动作快点
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.66,0:08:49.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.42,0:08:52.86,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,妈妈 给我2钱
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.95,0:08:54.59,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我铅笔掉了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.65,0:08:56.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在发零花钱前给我忍下
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.57,0:09:00.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你别再乱画画不就得了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.06,0:09:05.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,澄 我跟你换支铅笔吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.67,0:09:06.17,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.27,0:09:07.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.20,0:09:10.06,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,水原家的哲 每天都有去学校吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.34,0:09:11.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯？有来呀
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.56,0:09:18.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.25,0:09:19.21,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.02,0:09:38.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.67,0:09:42.12,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好短
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.61,0:09:44.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不知道这样能不能撑过这周
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.17,0:09:47.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这次别丢了才行
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.96,0:09:52.93,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,今天的画是自由画
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.36,0:09:55.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,交了的人就可以回去了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.70,0:09:56.96,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.96,0:09:58.53,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要画哪里好呢
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.53,0:09:59.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哪里好呢
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.62,0:10:02.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯 不错哦
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.62,0:10:03.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不愧是你
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.60,0:10:06.76,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真好啊小铃 画这么好看
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.44,0:10:11.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.43,0:10:15.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那我去捡枯松叶了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.81,0:10:16.84,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.90,0:10:37.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,水原
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.81,0:10:41.33,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你再不画的话就回不去了哟
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.84,0:10:42.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我不回去
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.72,0:10:47.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,爸爸妈妈也不采海苔 只会喝酒
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.74,0:10:49.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我讨厌大海
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.84,0:10:50.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不画
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.32,0:10:52.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,浦野 手伸出来
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.34,0:10:57.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.77,0:10:58.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.96,0:11:02.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.45,0:11:05.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我哥哥的 我还有很多
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.66,0:11:07.29,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,兔子在跳着
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.12,0:11:11.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,正月的沉没事故发生时也是这样的大海
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.24,0:11:13.94,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要画的话你来画吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.44,0:11:15.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,画这个无趣的大海
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.99,0:11:22.30,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,水原 你刚刚说的是什么意思
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.29,0:11:27.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,白浪就像跳动的兔子一样
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.72,0:11:31.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,水原 给你加上哥哥吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.55,0:11:32.22,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.22,0:11:35.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,给你哥哥看见的话要全速逃跑
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.90,0:11:37.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我们男生间有这样的规定
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.08,0:11:43.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不过…也比进入海军学校
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.21,0:11:46.50,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然后在海里溺死的笨蛋要好
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.07,0:11:51.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真的诶 就像白色的兔子一样
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.31,0:11:54.98,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯 画好了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.52,0:11:56.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,帮你捡好了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.80,0:11:57.93,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.87,0:12:01.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,很好哦 画得真棒
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.58,0:12:04.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,既然都画好了那只能回去了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.94,0:12:06.86,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这样的画
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.82,0:12:09.58,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不就讨厌不起这个海了
