Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.40,0:12:20.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,于东太平洋全海域作战中的帝国海军部队
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.81,0:12:23.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,万岁 万岁
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.54,0:12:24.74,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.53,0:12:30.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,森田家的侄女 这边早点采比较好哦
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.19,0:12:31.45,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.91,0:12:36.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,挺棒的决战服嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.80,0:12:40.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.06,0:12:41.35,kono-text-cn-2,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.10,0:12:54.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,越做越好了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.96,0:12:57.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,也正好了那来吃午饭
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.18,0:12:59.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.90,0:13:00.98,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好远
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.65,0:13:02.14,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.60,0:13:05.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃姐会嫁到好远的地方去
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.68,0:13:06.60,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.21,0:13:08.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,澄姐就很近
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.93,0:13:14.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,筷子拿得比较远的人会嫁到远处
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.22,0:13:18.06,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,奶奶是从哪嫁过来的
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.24,0:13:21.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我是从古江嫁过来的
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.16,0:13:25.11,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,从隔壁的古江到草津都这样了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.23,0:13:28.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那嫁到满洲等地方的人岂不是火筷子都不够长了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.93,0:13:32.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你一边这么说却一边拿远了筷子
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.21,0:13:35.52,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嫁太近不就没什么追求了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.15,0:13:41.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃 马上回去
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.03,0:13:44.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,接了个电话 我还以为是什么
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.87,0:13:48.05,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,有人到你家说要娶你了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.18,0:13:49.59,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,专门从吴市过来
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.72,0:13:50.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,吴市？
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.81,0:13:54.21,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃 你几岁了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.27,0:13:55.40,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,19
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.79,0:13:58.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,周岁的话18
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.79,0:14:01.05,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不喜欢的话拒绝就行了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.18,0:14:02.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,稍微过去看下
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.83,0:14:05.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃 稍微过来下
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.83,0:14:12.17,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,为了你总有一天会成为新娘而准备的
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.90,0:14:15.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,能合身就好了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.10,0:14:19.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.42,0:14:21.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.66,0:14:24.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然后要和那边办婚礼对吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.60,0:14:26.22,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.22,0:14:31.22,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那天晚上新郎会问你「带伞了吗」
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.32,0:14:36.92,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然后你就说「带了一把新的」
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.56,0:14:41.05,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然后如果他说「可以给我吗」
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.16,0:14:43.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你就说「请便」 听到了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.21,0:14:45.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.32,0:14:46.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,没有为什么
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.63,0:14:48.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我好像要成为大人了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.69,0:14:53.28,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,说到吴市的话 就是有军港的地方吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.87,0:14:56.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,有很多水兵
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.95,0:15:03.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,水原
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.03,0:15:06.42,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.69,0:15:08.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,早点去家里吧
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.17,0:15:08.60,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.98,0:15:12.23,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你的妈妈吓了一跳 在吵吵闹闹的
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.42,0:15:13.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,邻居都知道了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.28,0:15:17.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,吓死了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.83,0:15:19.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我差点以为是你
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.89,0:15:20.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你傻吗
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.80,0:15:25.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我是因为哥哥七周年忌辰这个庄重的理由回来的
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.01,0:15:30.56,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你不认识对方吗
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.29,0:15:32.07,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不认识
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.83,0:15:35.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,可能是把我和澄弄错了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.37,0:15:38.51,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,澄也比较漂亮
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.60,0:15:41.52,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我倒觉得不是这样
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.47,0:15:45.30,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,他是在这边的学校上学的时候
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.37,0:15:47.84,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不知道在哪遇到的
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.06,0:15:51.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,为了找到你们真是费了好大力
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.25,0:15:55.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我家也因为三年前江波冲町的填海造路
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.79,0:15:57.86,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不再采海苔了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.15,0:16:01.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不过应该可以恢复以前的样子了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.49,0:16:05.23,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,虽然我也不知道到底是不是好事
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.68,0:16:10.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不过感觉口中有焦糖的味道 是为什么呢
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.26,0:16:12.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.42,0:16:15.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,难办了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.97,0:16:18.52,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,虽然说不喜欢也可以拒绝
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.09,0:16:21.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不过我也不知道我喜不喜欢他
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.91,0:16:22.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.20,0:16:24.93,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.82,0:16:28.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我们迷路了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.06,0:16:30.96,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,电车站是哪里呢
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.53,0:16:32.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在这边
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.43,0:16:33.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.78,0:16:37.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,虽然有个亲切的水兵告诉了我
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.09,0:16:41.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,他也是个很稀奇的人
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.71,0:16:46.47,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好像在山中给个很稀奇的女性带路平安回去了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.86,0:16:54.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我真的有那么迷糊吗
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.19,0:16:53.61,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs50\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5\pos(337,160)\3c&H868686&}1944
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.19,0:16:53.61,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5\pos(313,208)\3c&H868686&}年
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.19,0:16:53.61,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs60\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5\pos(335,302)\3c&H868686&}2
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.19,0:16:53.61,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5\pos(309,347.224)\3c&H868686&}月
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.54,0:16:58.57,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什么时候变成这样的呢
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.73,0:17:09.84,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.93,0:17:14.82,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,接下来请将靠海一侧的百叶窗关上
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.32,0:17:26.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哪里的窗开着
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.45,0:17:33.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,吴市 吴市
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.73,0:17:38.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是海军们的炮台训练吧
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.68,0:17:53.79,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真的不好意思
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.80,0:17:55.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我觉得很适合哦
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.88,0:18:00.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,木炭巴士不会开上来对吧
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.01,0:18:02.14,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 小林夫人
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.14,0:18:03.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.11,0:18:07.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,小林夫人 今天就拜托了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.43,0:18:09.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,天气也不错真是太好了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.17,0:18:13.21,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,今后承您照顾
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.66,0:18:15.92,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,小女子不才 今后会尽孝的
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.92,0:18:18.51,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我是周作的伯母小林
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.80,0:18:20.96,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是作为你们的媒人
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.10,0:18:24.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,她到底知不知道自己将来嫁给的人的名字
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.10,0:18:26.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真的不才啊 到底行不行啊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.09,0:18:37.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要走这么高上来啊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.88,0:18:40.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这里是附近最角落的地方了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.33,0:18:41.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.25,0:18:43.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,过来了哦
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.54,0:18:47.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在这个年代万事都要从简非常抱歉
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.80,0:18:49.29,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我家的孩子有点怯场
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.30,0:18:50.19,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.92,0:18:51.98,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 不好
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.19,0:18:54.45,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,难得好看的衣服要白费了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.80,0:18:59.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,喂 铃 你在哪里脱衣服啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.93,0:19:08.93,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这还真是丰盛呢
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.93,0:19:11.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这孩子的哥哥没能来真是太可惜了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.98,0:19:14.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真的来了不少人呢
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.74,0:19:19.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,吃多点 这可是把晚上的份也拿出来了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.05,0:19:22.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这个炖菜煮的很好嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.91,0:19:26.93,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,太好了呢 是个挺老实的人
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.32,0:19:29.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,没人会在这种场合乱来吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.48,0:19:30.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你不就乱来了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.67,0:19:35.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那回娘家的时候再见了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.50,0:19:37.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好 再见
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.43,0:19:40.56,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我还会再来的
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.41,0:19:49.28,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那个…是谁来着
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.34,0:19:50.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,新娘也嫁过来了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.10,0:19:54.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,家里的事都交给她 你就悠闲地睡吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.73,0:19:55.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.22,0:20:01.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,爸爸 妈妈 今后就承您们照顾了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.63,0:20:03.79,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不 我们才是
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.14,0:20:06.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我的脚一直疼
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.12,0:20:09.29,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就拜托你了 铃
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.91,0:20:10.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.86,0:20:13.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.31,0:20:15.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,径子煮饭老是会焦掉
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.07,0:20:20.29,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 那个是嫁走了的姐姐吗
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.93,0:20:40.47,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是军舰的照射训练
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.48,0:20:41.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.82,0:20:45.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我到底是从哪边过来的
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.71,0:20:55.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,被子 谢谢你帮我铺好了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.29,0:20:56.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.65,0:21:02.82,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,对了 铃
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.31,0:21:03.96,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.19,0:21:07.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,带伞了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.80,0:21:15.57,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是 带了一把新的
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.81,0:21:18.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,稍微借我一下
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.63,0:21:26.23,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.81,0:21:30.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,肚子饿了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.14,0:21:35.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什么嘛 还是涩的
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.85,0:21:40.57,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你 白天的时候什么都没吃对吧
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.30,0:21:44.23,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,原来你会好好用嘴巴吃饭 我放心了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.13,0:21:47.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,放心吧放心吧
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.79,0:21:49.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,刚刚连种子都吞下去了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.89,0:21:51.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好好从嘴巴吃的
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.22,0:21:54.23,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.41,0:21:56.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我们以前 在哪里见过吗
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.78,0:22:01.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,见过哦 你不记得了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.63,0:22:05.60,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,对不起 我本来就比较迷糊
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.66,0:22:07.56,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你从以前开始就是这样
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.74,0:22:12.47,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然后 以前也是 这里有颗黑痣
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.81,0:22:49.43,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,水井在下面 是和邻组共用的
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.56,0:22:50.12,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 1,0:23:15.74,0:23:20.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,北…条…
Dialogue: 1,0:23:28.11,0:23:29.28,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 1,0:23:29.95,0:23:35.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这里是吴市的什么町的几号来着
Dialogue: 1,0:23:37.16,0:23:37.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,0:23:37.95,0:23:38.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那再见
Dialogue: 1,0:23:39.69,0:23:40.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,一路走好
Dialogue: 1,0:23:42.46,0:23:46.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这附近的人都是当海兵的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:23:56.70,0:23:58.07,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,北条夫人
Dialogue: 1,0:24:01.62,0:24:02.94,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,北条夫人
Dialogue: 1,0:24:02.95,0:24:04.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:24:04.08,0:24:08.09,kono-hmz,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正稚艺_GBK\fs55\frz257.7\c&H777B7D&\pos(1208,618)}二月二十四日的配给值班
Dialogue: 1,0:24:04.08,0:24:08.09,kono-hmz,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正稚艺_GBK\fs55\frz257.7\c&H777B7D&\pos(1070,594)}知多 北条 刈谷
Dialogue: 1,0:24:04.08,0:24:08.09,kono-hmz,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正稚艺_GBK\fs55\frz257.7\c&H777B7D&\pos(914,558)}例会的通知
Dialogue: 1,0:24:04.08,0:24:08.09,kono-hmz,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正稚艺_GBK\fs45\frz257.7\c&H777B7D&\pos(776.032,579.969)}二十四日（星期四）午后七点
Dialogue: 1,0:24:04.08,0:24:08.09,kono-hmz,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正稚艺_GBK\fs45\c&H777B7D&\frz255\pos(669.845,539.527)}于中长之木邻保馆
Dialogue: 1,0:24:04.30,0:24:05.71,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,配给的值班？
Dialogue: 1,0:24:05.71,0:24:10.33,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这个和这个 一直都是这样
Dialogue: 1,0:24:10.81,0:24:12.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,承您照顾了
Dialogue: 1,0:24:12.55,0:24:13.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我是知多
Dialogue: 1,0:24:13.32,0:24:14.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我是刈谷
Dialogue: 1,0:24:19.56,0:24:20.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,喂 你又这样
Dialogue: 1,0:24:20.91,0:24:22.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我不是好好量着吗
Dialogue: 1,0:24:23.11,0:24:25.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你不是按目测来的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:24:25.15,0:24:25.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 1,0:24:25.85,0:24:27.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,会不公平的
Dialogue: 1,0:24:27.04,0:24:28.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不会
Dialogue: 1,0:24:28.35,0:24:29.23,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 1,0:24:29.63,0:24:30.56,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:24:30.68,0:24:33.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你就是这个地方不行
Dialogue: 1,0:24:33.45,0:24:34.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哪点
Dialogue: 1,0:24:35.11,0:24:36.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我还年轻
Dialogue: 1,0:24:36.82,0:24:38.29,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要掉下来了
Dialogue: 1,0:24:45.49,0:24:46.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 1,0:24:47.17,0:24:50.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,必须指出其威力非常之大
Dialogue: 1,0:24:50.64,0:24:52.82,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,如果燃烧弹被投放的话
Dialogue: 1,0:24:53.07,0:24:56.71,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,首先必要的是随机应变
Dialogue: 1,0:24:57.44,0:24:59.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,再靠近点吧
Dialogue: 1,0:25:00.02,0:25:02.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这个座位可是很冷的
Dialogue: 1,0:25:03.37,0:25:03.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,0:25:05.65,0:25:08.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这些就是我的日常
Dialogue: 1,0:25:09.27,0:25:14.74,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs50\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(337,160)}1944
Dialogue: 1,0:25:09.27,0:25:14.74,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(313,208)}年
Dialogue: 1,0:25:09.27,0:25:14.74,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs60\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(335,302)}3
Dialogue: 1,0:25:09.27,0:25:14.74,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(309,347.224)}月
Dialogue: 1,0:25:19.85,0:25:23.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 那是径子还没出嫁前的衣服
Dialogue: 1,0:25:23.60,0:25:25.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那件也放仓库里吧
Dialogue: 1,0:25:25.72,0:25:30.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,她和未婚夫出去的时候就会穿这件衣服
Dialogue: 1,0:25:30.42,0:25:35.06,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,去看电影 吃洋食 看博览会
Dialogue: 1,0:25:37.50,0:25:40.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,姐姐是个摩登女郎啊
Dialogue: 1,0:25:41.21,0:25:43.93,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那时候还不是现在这样的年代
Dialogue: 1,0:25:44.95,0:25:46.76,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,周作四年级的时候
Dialogue: 1,0:25:47.04,0:25:50.79,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,为了和平的军事缩减导致造不了军舰
Dialogue: 1,0:25:47.04,0:25:50.79,kono-text-cn - tips,,0,0,0,,注：指的是《华盛顿海军条约》
Dialogue: 1,0:25:52.03,0:25:55.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我们家和这附近的人大多失业了
Dialogue: 1,0:25:56.03,0:25:57.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真是不得了
Dialogue: 1,0:25:58.39,0:26:00.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,径子就是那样的孩子
Dialogue: 1,0:26:00.62,0:26:04.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,工作也是自己决定 丈夫也是自己找
Dialogue: 1,0:26:06.47,0:26:09.23,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,既然如此我也要不认输地努力工作了
Dialogue: 1,0:26:11.14,0:26:14.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那个时候真是不得了
Dialogue: 1,0:26:14.86,0:26:15.76,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 1,0:26:15.76,0:26:18.93,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真是怀念的不得了的那个时候
Dialogue: 1,0:26:28.00,0:26:29.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 你好
Dialogue: 1,0:26:30.70,0:26:31.56,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 1,0:26:31.93,0:26:34.84,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 欢迎回来 姐姐
Dialogue: 1,0:26:37.96,0:26:38.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,简朴
Dialogue: 1,0:26:41.26,0:26:44.82,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,简朴什么的 现在大米也是挺贵重的东西
Dialogue: 1,0:26:45.14,0:26:46.17,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我是说你
Dialogue: 1,0:26:47.26,0:26:50.59,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你是广岛来的我还以为你有多上流
Dialogue: 1,0:26:51.09,0:26:53.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你那缝缝补补的裤子是怎么回事
Dialogue: 1,0:26:54.36,0:26:56.06,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你在炒豆子吗
Dialogue: 1,0:26:56.24,0:26:58.76,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哎呀晴美 欢迎来哦
Dialogue: 1,0:26:58.89,0:27:01.96,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,妈妈经常会心情不好
Dialogue: 1,0:27:02.40,0:27:03.96,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,所以晴美有乖哦
Dialogue: 1,0:27:03.96,0:27:07.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,对不起 我现在只有这件
Dialogue: 1,0:27:07.34,0:27:08.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,再作一件 马上
Dialogue: 1,0:27:13.02,0:27:15.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,还有那袋大米不是礼物
Dialogue: 1,0:27:15.34,0:27:17.07,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是我和女儿的份
Dialogue: 1,0:27:19.23,0:27:20.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然后 径子
Dialogue: 1,0:27:21.00,0:27:22.57,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你听我说啦 妈妈
Dialogue: 1,0:27:22.57,0:27:25.56,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哎呀 现在难办了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:27:27.49,0:27:27.96,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 1,0:27:28.37,0:27:30.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你又来了 错了错了
Dialogue: 1,0:27:31.08,0:27:34.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你这么笨可是嫁不出去的
Dialogue: 1,0:27:34.65,0:27:36.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不理了 我不嫁了
Dialogue: 1,0:27:43.97,0:27:47.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那个 腰的地方是
Dialogue: 1,0:27:48.21,0:27:49.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 原来如此
Dialogue: 1,0:28:05.10,0:28:07.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,把这个解开
Dialogue: 1,0:28:07.70,0:28:09.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,再裁剪一下
Dialogue: 1,0:28:09.62,0:28:11.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,合在一起 缝起来
Dialogue: 1,0:28:12.93,0:28:15.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,穿上橡皮筋就做好了
Dialogue: 1,0:28:15.72,0:28:16.64,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 1,0:28:20.33,0:28:21.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我是黑村晴美
Dialogue: 1,0:28:21.87,0:28:23.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我是北条铃 你好
Dialogue: 1,0:28:25.37,0:28:27.19,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃 给我绳子
Dialogue: 1,0:28:28.31,0:28:29.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这个可以吗
Dialogue: 1,0:28:47.16,0:28:49.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃 你去买东西吗
Dialogue: 1,0:28:49.26,0:28:50.76,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,对 去配给所
Dialogue: 1,0:28:51.47,0:28:54.96,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我去吧 配给票和钱包给我吧
Dialogue: 1,0:28:55.50,0:28:57.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这样吗 拜托了
Dialogue: 1,0:29:12.31,0:29:13.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 1,0:29:18.81,0:29:20.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,够了 我来做
Dialogue: 1,0:29:30.02,0:29:32.23,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我说 妈妈
Dialogue: 1,0:29:34.51,0:29:35.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,来了来了
Dialogue: 1,0:29:36.24,0:29:37.07,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 1,0:29:37.07,0:29:38.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就是汤的料来着
Dialogue: 1,0:29:57.11,0:30:00.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,径子和晴美来了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:30:00.46,0:30:01.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,两个人吗
Dialogue: 1,0:30:01.49,0:30:02.96,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 父亲
Dialogue: 1,0:30:03.05,0:30:04.82,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在这里多待一会吧
Dialogue: 1,0:30:06.91,0:30:11.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真少见 姐姐烧的饭居然没怎么烧焦
Dialogue: 1,0:30:11.83,0:30:13.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你说什么 周作
Dialogue: 1,0:30:13.50,0:30:15.86,kono-text-cn-2,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 1,0:30:13.75,0:30:15.86,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那个 姐姐
Dialogue: 1,0:30:16.27,0:30:19.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,多亏了你的帮忙 和服改好了
Dialogue: 1,0:30:20.49,0:30:22.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 1,0:30:22.78,0:30:25.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,因为母亲的脚也不是很方便
Dialogue: 1,0:30:25.54,0:30:29.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,像你这样的孩子突然间被带到一个陌生的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:30:29.94,0:30:33.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要是我一直待在这里就好了
Dialogue: 1,0:30:34.40,0:30:37.86,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃 你不如回广岛吧
Dialogue: 1,0:30:40.81,0:30:41.92,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那样也好
Dialogue: 1,0:30:47.42,0:30:48.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 1,0:30:49.17,0:30:50.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好累呀
Dialogue: 1,0:30:50.89,0:30:51.93,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 1,0:30:52.92,0:30:54.74,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,已经八点了
Dialogue: 1,0:30:54.95,0:30:56.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,今天也很多呀
Dialogue: 1,0:30:58.25,0:30:59.84,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这全都是千人针吗
Dialogue: 1,0:30:58.25,0:30:59.84,kono-text-cn - tips,,0,0,0,,注：为了祝愿出征军人保命免灾，由一千个女人,在一块白布上,用红线每人各缝一针制成的腰带
Dialogue: 1,0:30:59.87,0:31:02.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是呀 澄 等下你也要帮忙缝一下
Dialogue: 1,0:31:04.18,0:31:06.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,喂铃 该起来了
Dialogue: 1,0:31:06.80,0:31:08.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 1,0:31:10.36,0:31:12.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,给 该吃晚饭了
Dialogue: 1,0:31:13.07,0:31:17.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,吓死我了 我做了一个远嫁吴市的梦
Dialogue: 1,0:31:19.67,0:31:21.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,醒来了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:31:20.72,0:31:21.31,kono-text-cn-2,,0,0,0,,醒了
Dialogue: 1,0:31:21.97,0:31:26.05,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然后 姐姐就跟我说让我回广岛去
Dialogue: 1,0:31:27.16,0:31:29.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我就在想这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 1,0:31:29.65,0:31:31.11,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 回娘家呀
Dialogue: 1,0:31:31.85,0:31:33.93,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然后公公婆婆就说
Dialogue: 1,0:31:34.41,0:31:36.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,「一直以来没注意到你的想法真的很抱歉」
Dialogue: 1,0:31:37.85,0:31:41.05,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,「回去好好休息两三天吧」
Dialogue: 1,0:31:41.30,0:31:42.17,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,姐姐也说
Dialogue: 1,0:31:43.81,0:31:46.76,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,既然你都这样说了 也挺好的不是么
Dialogue: 1,0:31:48.10,0:31:50.60,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,说起来 给要一寄了明信片没有
Dialogue: 1,0:31:50.69,0:31:52.01,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我么 已经寄了
Dialogue: 1,0:31:52.58,0:31:54.84,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,但…还没有回复
Dialogue: 1,0:31:55.92,0:31:57.42,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,家里也是么
Dialogue: 1,0:31:59.77,0:32:01.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嘛 毕竟这么远
Dialogue: 1,0:32:01.09,0:32:03.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,毕竟鬼哥哥不爱动笔
Dialogue: 1,0:32:03.75,0:32:06.52,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,也可能是铃把地址写错了
Dialogue: 1,0:32:07.73,0:32:09.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,洗澡去 洗澡去
Dialogue: 1,0:32:09.99,0:32:12.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,澄在挺身队那边怎么样
Dialogue: 1,0:32:09.99,0:32:12.02,kono-text-cn - tips,,0,0,0,,注：挺身队根据是1944年8月颁布的法令组成的女子劳工，朝鲜境内的慰安妇也被称为「挺身队」
Dialogue: 1,0:32:12.03,0:32:13.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,基本上习惯了
Dialogue: 1,0:32:13.67,0:32:15.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我全身都是机油臭味对吧
Dialogue: 1,0:32:16.39,0:32:19.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那都是些危险的工作 真辛苦你了
Dialogue: 1,0:32:19.52,0:32:22.53,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,虽说如此 但也没有做海苔那样寒冷
Dialogue: 1,0:32:22.64,0:32:23.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,也是有好事情发生的
Dialogue: 1,0:32:24.25,0:32:28.90,kono-text-cn - tips,,0,0,0,,注：将校泛指少尉以上的军官
Dialogue: 1,0:32:24.25,0:32:28.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,有个很帅的将校先生偷偷地把食堂的食券塞给我
Dialogue: 1,0:32:28.90,0:32:30.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 1,0:32:30.23,0:32:32.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,没想到一不小心知道了陆军的秘密了
Dialogue: 1,0:32:33.33,0:32:34.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃呢 你怎么样
Dialogue: 1,0:32:35.43,0:32:36.79,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,吴市那有什么好事发生吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:32:38.58,0:32:40.93,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要记的东西有很多 所以还没有
Dialogue: 1,0:32:42.74,0:32:46.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我好像一不小心
Dialogue: 1,0:32:46.27,0:32:49.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,触碰到了海军的秘密
Dialogue: 1,0:32:49.46,0:32:50.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什…什么
Dialogue: 1,0:32:50.39,0:32:51.14,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,快睡吧
Dialogue: 1,0:32:53.62,0:32:54.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 1,0:32:54.85,0:32:55.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 1,0:32:56.32,0:32:58.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你貌似有点秃了
Dialogue: 1,0:33:01.29,0:33:04.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,再见 铃 我出门了
Dialogue: 1,0:33:05.22,0:33:07.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,根据战时特殊措施
Dialogue: 1,0:33:07.25,0:33:10.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,下个月的时候短期外出也会受到限制
Dialogue: 1,0:33:11.34,0:33:12.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,请多保重
Dialogue: 1,0:33:13.80,0:33:16.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我也要去妇人会那里帮忙了
Dialogue: 1,0:33:16.83,0:33:19.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,妈妈也要出门吗
Dialogue: 1,0:33:34.42,0:33:37.53,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,爸爸给了我一些零用钱
Dialogue: 1,0:34:09.53,0:34:10.45,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 1,0:34:12.43,0:34:13.86,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,再见了 广岛
Dialogue: 1,0:34:18.70,0:34:20.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正少儿_gbk\fs40\bord0\c&H6C6F73&\frz275.7\pos(1070.506,460.236)}今天的车票已经全部{\c&H6F75AA&}卖光
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.70,0:34:20.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正少儿_gbk\fs40\bord0\c&H6C6F73&\frz275.7\pos(747.036,343.346)}广岛站
Dialogue: 1,0:34:20.45,0:34:22.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然后你就回来了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:34:23.03,0:34:25.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,对他们家实在是太不好意思了
Dialogue: 1,0:34:33.72,0:34:35.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 1,0:34:36.17,0:34:42.26,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs50\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5\pos(337,160)\3c&H868686&}1944
Dialogue: 1,0:34:36.17,0:34:42.26,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5\pos(313,208)\3c&H868686&}年
Dialogue: 1,0:34:36.17,0:34:42.26,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs60\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5\pos(335,302)\3c&H868686&}4
Dialogue: 1,0:34:36.17,0:34:42.26,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5\pos(309,347.224)\3c&H868686&}月
Dialogue: 1,0:34:37.54,0:34:39.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,姐姐她一直都在家里
Dialogue: 1,0:34:43.82,0:34:45.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 1,0:34:45.32,0:34:47.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,借一下砚台给我吧
Dialogue: 1,0:34:47.33,0:34:48.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,为啥 晴美
Dialogue: 1,0:34:49.62,0:34:51.07,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,借给我吧
Dialogue: 1,0:34:51.70,0:34:55.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃 你跟晴美说什么了
Dialogue: 1,0:34:57.12,0:35:00.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我能把传阅板报给下一家了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:35:00.37,0:35:01.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 1,0:35:02.92,0:35:03.98,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我出门了
Dialogue: 1,0:35:04.35,0:35:07.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,自从从广岛回来后就一直这个样子了
Dialogue: 1,0:35:08.45,0:35:10.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,由她去吧 她还只是个孩子
Dialogue: 1,0:35:10.45,0:35:12.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 1,0:35:14.78,0:35:16.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我都说了不可以
Dialogue: 1,0:35:16.64,0:35:17.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,借给我吧
Dialogue: 1,0:35:18.34,0:35:21.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你根本不需要这个吧
Dialogue: 1,0:35:45.36,0:35:46.28,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 1,0:35:48.20,0:35:49.98,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在摘野草啊
Dialogue: 1,0:35:51.45,0:35:53.79,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我想着摘一些来当晚饭的配菜
Dialogue: 1,0:35:55.76,0:35:58.45,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这附近的蒲公英都是白色的呢
Dialogue: 1,0:35:59.08,0:36:00.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,江波那边的不一样么
Dialogue: 1,0:36:01.50,0:36:03.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,也有些黄色的呢
Dialogue: 1,0:36:06.64,0:36:08.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,可能是从很遥远的地方来的
Dialogue: 1,0:36:10.82,0:36:13.52,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什么嘛 我见你没什么精神
Dialogue: 1,0:36:13.81,0:36:15.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,原来是思念家乡了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:36:15.78,0:36:16.76,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 1,0:36:23.48,0:36:25.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,快看那边
Dialogue: 1,0:36:25.45,0:36:27.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,今天还有航空母舰呢
Dialogue: 1,0:36:27.58,0:36:29.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,应该是飞鹰和隼鹰吧
Dialogue: 1,0:36:29.59,0:36:30.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真大
Dialogue: 1,0:36:32.21,0:36:34.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然后在那边小小的都是驱逐舰
Dialogue: 1,0:36:34.87,0:36:36.86,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,连德国进口的U型潜艇也有
Dialogue: 1,0:36:37.23,0:36:40.58,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,而那个看起来很普通的船是潜水母舰
Dialogue: 1,0:36:45.49,0:36:47.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,看 绣眼鸟在天上飞
Dialogue: 1,0:36:48.44,0:36:50.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在那里 那里 快看
Dialogue: 1,0:36:50.77,0:36:51.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我看到了
Dialogue: 1,0:36:54.25,0:36:57.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,周作 那是什么
Dialogue: 1,0:36:57.78,0:36:59.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是船吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:36:59.71,0:37:00.59,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那个是大和
Dialogue: 1,0:37:01.75,0:37:05.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,产自东洋第一的军港 世界第一的军舰
Dialogue: 1,0:37:06.13,0:37:08.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在那艘船上也载有人吗
Dialogue: 1,0:37:09.24,0:37:09.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:37:13.09,0:37:14.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,大概有两千七百人
Dialogue: 1,0:37:14.92,0:37:17.00,kono-text-cn-2,,0,0,0,,注意前行 注意前行
Dialogue: 1,0:37:18.05,0:37:20.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,两千七百人
Dialogue: 1,0:37:21.39,0:37:22.43,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:37:22.90,0:37:25.19,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃 对他们说「欢迎回来吴市」吧
Dialogue: 1,0:37:27.77,0:37:31.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,每天都要在那样的地方给这么多人煮饭吗
Dialogue: 1,0:37:31.95,0:37:32.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 1,0:37:32.46,0:37:33.64,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那洗衣服呢？
Dialogue: 1,0:37:38.92,0:37:41.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,对不起 你没事吧
Dialogue: 1,0:37:41.86,0:37:42.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 1,0:37:43.44,0:37:44.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你没受伤吧
Dialogue: 1,0:37:54.55,0:37:55.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我说啊 铃
Dialogue: 1,0:37:56.08,0:37:58.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,太过于在意的话 秃头只会变得越来越严重的啦
Dialogue: 1,0:37:59.18,0:38:00.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,被你发现了呀
Dialogue: 1,0:38:01.40,0:38:03.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,借我笔吧
Dialogue: 1,0:38:03.49,0:38:06.28,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我想帮铃阿姨的头上涂下墨水
Dialogue: 1,0:38:06.40,0:38:07.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我说了不行
Dialogue: 1,0:38:07.78,0:38:10.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你不是已经把那一片都弄黑了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:38:12.79,0:38:16.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在这之后 姐姐回婆家去了
Dialogue: 1,0:38:16.82,0:38:19.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,接下来该我开始准备煮饭了
Dialogue: 1,0:38:19.75,0:38:22.93,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,正当我这么想的时候 配给量已经大量减少
Dialogue: 1,0:38:20.15,0:38:24.90,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs50\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5\pos(337,160)\3c&H868686&}1944
Dialogue: 1,0:38:20.15,0:38:24.90,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5\pos(313,208)\3c&H868686&}年
Dialogue: 1,0:38:20.15,0:38:24.90,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs60\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5\pos(335,302)\3c&H868686&}5
Dialogue: 1,0:38:20.15,0:38:24.90,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5\pos(309,347.224)\3c&H868686&}月
Dialogue: 1,0:38:24.21,0:38:28.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,四条沙丁鱼干要作为一家四口三餐的量
Dialogue: 1,0:38:29.68,0:38:32.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嘛 也比只有青菜叶的日子要好了
Dialogue: 1,0:38:32.44,0:38:35.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在这里排队的话总会买到豆腐渣的
Dialogue: 1,0:38:32.03,0:38:36.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正少儿_gbk\fs40\bord0\c&H6C6F73&\pos(629.058,670.303)}今天有豆腐渣
Dialogue: 1,0:38:36.59,0:38:37.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 1,0:38:39.51,0:38:43.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,堇菜 繁缕 杉菜
Dialogue: 1,0:38:44.11,0:38:49.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,蒲公英 酢浆草 沙丁鱼干 豆腐渣 马铃薯 红薯
Dialogue: 1,0:38:49.85,0:38:51.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,小麦粉 梅子干的种子
Dialogue: 1,0:38:54.85,0:38:57.42,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,先把红薯切开 蒸煮
Dialogue: 1,0:38:57.82,0:39:00.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,轻微白灼一下杉菜 晾干水分后切碎
Dialogue: 1,0:39:01.22,0:39:03.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,用小麦粉把芋头和杉菜混合起来
Dialogue: 1,0:39:03.98,0:39:05.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,简单揉成团
Dialogue: 1,0:39:05.40,0:39:07.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,中午饭就这样做好啦
Dialogue: 1,0:39:07.18,0:39:09.50,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,径子她们不在就显得好安静呢
Dialogue: 1,0:39:09.84,0:39:12.05,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,剩下的就晒干保存起来
Dialogue: 1,0:39:13.73,0:39:14.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,接下来还有
Dialogue: 1,0:39:15.70,0:39:18.98,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,用五倍的水来把米煮成稀粥
Dialogue: 1,0:39:19.86,0:39:23.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,加入马铃薯滚刀块再煮上十分钟
Dialogue: 1,0:39:24.06,0:39:26.01,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,随后加切碎的繁缕
Dialogue: 1,0:39:26.77,0:39:29.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,萝卜皮 蒲公英的根部
Dialogue: 1,0:39:29.62,0:39:32.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,细切成丝后加入砂糖和酱油炖煮
Dialogue: 1,0:39:32.96,0:39:35.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,加上切碎的蒲公英叶子
Dialogue: 1,0:39:35.42,0:39:37.59,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,最后加入豆腐渣炖煮
Dialogue: 1,0:39:39.69,0:39:43.50,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,萝卜切薄 加入盐和酢浆草混匀
Dialogue: 1,0:39:45.40,0:39:47.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,把梅子干的种子和水放入锅中
Dialogue: 1,0:39:47.94,0:39:50.57,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,当沸腾的时候再加入沙丁鱼干
Dialogue: 1,0:39:50.89,0:39:53.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不要盖上盖子 不停用汤汁浇盖在上面
Dialogue: 1,0:39:53.68,0:39:55.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,煮好后放盐调味
Dialogue: 1,0:39:55.68,0:39:59.21,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这个是刈谷教的做法
Dialogue: 1,0:39:59.28,0:40:01.74,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,但是大米的配给只有一半而已
Dialogue: 1,0:40:02.02,0:40:03.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,所以只能吃放多点芋头做的稀饭
Dialogue: 1,0:40:03.84,0:40:04.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,没事啦
Dialogue: 1,0:40:04.88,0:40:06.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,接下来 明天也包在我身上吧
Dialogue: 1,0:40:07.84,0:40:10.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这是忠臣楠木公为了固守城池时撑更久
Dialogue: 1,0:40:07.84,0:40:10.62,kono-text-cn - tips,,0,0,0,,注：楠木正成 为镰仓幕府末期到南北朝时期著名武将
Dialogue: 1,0:40:10.82,0:40:13.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,而发明出的粮食增量法
Dialogue: 1,0:40:15.57,0:40:18.23,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,首先 把大米仔细翻炒
Dialogue: 1,0:40:19.34,0:40:23.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,加入三倍的水量 用文火慢慢煮透
Dialogue: 1,0:40:24.83,0:40:28.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不仅要节省大米的用量还要节省燃料
Dialogue: 1,0:40:28.81,0:40:33.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这时就要交给大日本帝国的利器 无火炉灶了
Dialogue: 1,0:40:34.90,0:40:36.22,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,等待过夜
Dialogue: 1,0:40:39.31,0:40:42.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,利用隔夜的煮鱼汤汁并加入堇菜
Dialogue: 1,0:40:42.89,0:40:44.45,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,拌入味噌直至煮沸
Dialogue: 1,0:40:45.51,0:40:48.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,再次点火煮沸米饭
Dialogue: 1,0:40:49.11,0:40:50.01,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,做好了
Dialogue: 1,0:40:50.70,0:40:53.71,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这就是源自楠木公的楠公饭了
Dialogue: 1,0:40:54.90,0:40:57.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这边是给父亲做的便当
Dialogue: 1,0:40:59.81,0:41:01.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,今早的饭量还真是多呢
Dialogue: 1,0:41:01.96,0:41:03.60,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,饭粒全都膨胀起来了
Dialogue: 1,0:41:03.93,0:41:06.14,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,原来还有这样的做法呢
Dialogue: 1,0:41:06.28,0:41:06.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 1,0:41:06.97,0:41:08.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 1,0:41:19.18,0:41:19.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我出门了
Dialogue: 1,0:41:19.81,0:41:20.64,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 1,0:41:20.81,0:41:23.94,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那样子也能吃得这么香的楠木公
Dialogue: 1,0:41:24.12,0:41:26.76,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,一定是一位了不起的豪杰呢
Dialogue: 1,0:41:27.56,0:41:29.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 1,0:41:29.29,0:41:34.63,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs50\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(337,160)}1944
Dialogue: 1,0:41:29.29,0:41:34.63,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(313,208)}年
Dialogue: 1,0:41:29.29,0:41:34.63,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs60\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(335,302)}6
Dialogue: 1,0:41:29.29,0:41:34.63,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(309,347.224)}月
Dialogue: 1,0:41:31.29,0:41:34.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,警戒警报发出
Dialogue: 1,0:41:36.25,0:41:39.42,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,空袭警报发出
Dialogue: 1,0:41:46.17,0:41:47.86,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,广播里面什么都没说
Dialogue: 1,0:41:48.51,0:41:50.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,周作已经出发去工作地点了么
Dialogue: 1,0:41:51.05,0:41:51.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 1,0:41:51.72,0:41:54.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,从敌人的预测续航能力来看
Dialogue: 1,0:41:54.92,0:41:57.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,第一次空袭选择九州是最好的
Dialogue: 1,0:41:57.62,0:42:00.21,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,从这里匆忙往山里逃去
Dialogue: 1,0:42:01.86,0:42:03.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,停电而已
Dialogue: 1,0:42:06.55,0:42:08.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你别掉下来哦
Dialogue: 1,0:42:09.12,0:42:11.08,kono-text-cn - tips,,0,0,0,,注：这里的疎開指当时日本为了防止空袭时大火蔓延烧毁重要设施而设立防火隔离带，称之为「建物疎開」
Dialogue: 1,0:42:09.12,0:42:11.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,建筑疏开啊
Dialogue: 1,0:42:12.10,0:42:14.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在市内扩建起了防火带
Dialogue: 1,0:42:15.79,0:42:18.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嘛 这里的话应该不用担心吧
Dialogue: 1,0:42:19.19,0:42:20.50,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真不容易啊
Dialogue: 1,0:42:21.08,0:42:23.43,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,大家已经找到了搬家的地点了么
Dialogue: 1,0:42:24.27,0:42:25.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 1,0:42:26.79,0:42:28.01,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不用谢
Dialogue: 1,0:42:29.61,0:42:31.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,柴火的话还有很多呢
Dialogue: 1,0:42:32.07,0:42:34.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我家被拆了
Dialogue: 1,0:42:36.35,0:42:39.05,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然后 我们一家就搬到了下关市去了
Dialogue: 1,0:42:39.91,0:42:41.84,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,机会正好 我就跟他离婚了
Dialogue: 1,0:42:41.97,0:42:42.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 1,0:42:43.72,0:42:47.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不用担心 我会找工作赚钱的
Dialogue: 1,0:42:48.07,0:42:50.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要进入的人数变多了
Dialogue: 1,0:42:51.74,0:42:52.71,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这样子么
Dialogue: 1,0:42:54.63,0:42:59.38,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs50\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(337,160)}1944
Dialogue: 1,0:42:54.63,0:42:59.38,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(313,208)}年
Dialogue: 1,0:42:54.63,0:42:59.38,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs60\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(335,302)}7
Dialogue: 1,0:42:54.63,0:42:59.38,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(309,347.224)}月
Dialogue: 1,0:42:58.78,0:43:01.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,昨天灰之峰上面也是响个不停呢
Dialogue: 1,0:43:02.03,0:43:04.76,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那样子的地方都有大炮打过来呢
Dialogue: 1,0:43:04.76,0:43:06.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真危险啊
Dialogue: 1,0:43:07.42,0:43:09.01,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 1,0:43:07.99,0:43:09.04,kono-text-cn-2,,0,0,0,,那 先走了
Dialogue: 1,0:43:09.92,0:43:13.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嘛 做出个挺好的防空洞不是么
Dialogue: 1,0:43:16.01,0:43:19.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,即使是加班加点做 也干劲十足的嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:43:20.25,0:43:24.58,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,从姐姐家拿来的柱子和榻榻米真是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 1,0:43:27.17,0:43:28.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,周作
Dialogue: 1,0:43:28.66,0:43:30.19,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你把它装在这里了呀
Dialogue: 1,0:43:31.01,0:43:32.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,没所谓了
Dialogue: 1,0:43:34.09,0:43:36.52,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然后再收拾一下外面吧
Dialogue: 1,0:43:39.17,0:43:40.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,周作
Dialogue: 1,0:43:40.66,0:43:44.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这些泥土拿去田地里可以么
Dialogue: 1,0:43:45.10,0:43:46.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,拿去吧拿去吧
Dialogue: 1,0:43:46.78,0:43:47.58,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,小心点
Dialogue: 1,0:43:48.43,0:43:50.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,呀 原来你在这里呀
Dialogue: 1,0:43:52.04,0:43:53.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,来看船
Dialogue: 1,0:43:56.32,0:43:58.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,今天也有一大堆船呢
Dialogue: 1,0:43:58.50,0:43:59.98,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,有两艘大和级船呢
Dialogue: 1,0:44:01.24,0:44:02.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,其中一个是武藏号
Dialogue: 1,0:44:03.05,0:44:07.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,虽然战舰有很多 航空母舰却不在
Dialogue: 1,0:44:08.34,0:44:10.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 那个是利根号
Dialogue: 1,0:44:10.41,0:44:14.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,尾部那里没有搭载炮台 是航空巡洋舰呢
Dialogue: 1,0:44:15.79,0:44:18.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真厉害啊 居然知道这么多
Dialogue: 1,0:44:19.02,0:44:21.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯 哥哥教会我的
Dialogue: 1,0:44:22.54,0:44:23.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 1,0:44:24.14,0:44:25.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我也有稍微学过一些
Dialogue: 1,0:44:26.76,0:44:27.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,驱逐舰
Dialogue: 1,0:44:28.49,0:44:30.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 好像有什么小小只的过来了
Dialogue: 1,0:44:31.30,0:44:32.65,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那是内火艇
Dialogue: 1,0:44:31.30,0:44:32.65,kono-text-cn - tips,,0,0,0,,注：即特二式内火艇，是一种两栖装甲战斗车
Dialogue: 1,0:44:34.62,0:44:36.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那么我作为回报
Dialogue: 1,0:44:37.42,0:44:39.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,很大一片云对吧
Dialogue: 1,0:44:40.09,0:44:41.84,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那叫做「砧状积雨云」
Dialogue: 1,0:44:43.40,0:44:44.84,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,看来要下大雨了
Dialogue: 1,0:44:49.37,0:44:50.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,周作
Dialogue: 1,0:44:50.10,0:44:52.76,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,总之先把那边的东西放进防空洞里吧
Dialogue: 1,0:45:02.50,0:45:03.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 1,0:45:10.80,0:45:12.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我自己来 我自己来
Dialogue: 1,0:45:13.73,0:45:15.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,还真是喜欢军舰呢
Dialogue: 1,0:45:16.51,0:45:18.17,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,听晴美说的
Dialogue: 1,0:45:19.92,0:45:21.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不是我教晴美的
Dialogue: 1,0:45:22.63,0:45:23.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,小久教的
Dialogue: 1,0:45:23.71,0:45:24.19,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,久？
Dialogue: 1,0:45:26.15,0:45:28.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯 很喜欢军舰的小久
Dialogue: 1,0:45:28.75,0:45:30.47,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,总有一天你也会见到他的
Dialogue: 1,0:45:31.29,0:45:32.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是这个
Dialogue: 1,0:45:32.80,0:45:34.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,叫「久夫」的人么
Dialogue: 1,0:45:35.21,0:45:35.84,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 1,0:45:46.90,0:45:48.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我和这个人
Dialogue: 1,0:45:48.58,0:45:50.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在做这样的事
Dialogue: 1,0:45:55.12,0:45:57.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好了 雨势也变小了
Dialogue: 1,0:45:58.27,0:45:59.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,现在就回去吧
Dialogue: 1,0:46:00.78,0:46:01.79,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 1,0:46:01.83,0:46:06.28,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嘛 都是夫妇了 能和睦相处是好事
Dialogue: 1,0:46:06.56,0:46:09.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 夫妇关系和睦是好事来的
Dialogue: 1,0:46:09.68,0:46:10.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,而且还有两对
Dialogue: 1,0:46:10.89,0:46:12.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,径子
Dialogue: 1,0:46:15.39,0:46:20.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,一家人整整齐齐 开开心心地量身高
Dialogue: 1,0:46:20.86,0:46:21.98,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,莫非
Dialogue: 1,0:46:22.47,0:46:25.84,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,姐姐她的丈夫…
Dialogue: 1,0:46:26.18,0:46:30.30,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,难得拥有一副可以不参军的瘦弱身体
Dialogue: 1,0:46:30.80,0:46:32.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,太瘦弱了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:46:33.89,0:46:37.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在父亲进入工厂再就职的时候
Dialogue: 1,0:46:37.76,0:46:40.17,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,姐姐为了庆祝他而跑去买时钟
Dialogue: 1,0:46:40.71,0:46:42.93,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就在那时候认识了那里的少爷
Dialogue: 1,0:46:44.20,0:46:45.42,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然后嫁给了他
Dialogue: 1,0:46:45.93,0:46:48.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,年轻夫妇两人翻新了店面
Dialogue: 1,0:46:49.76,0:46:53.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,但是 径子却是那样的性格
Dialogue: 1,0:46:53.55,0:46:55.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,与公公婆婆的关系又有很多矛盾
Dialogue: 1,0:46:56.53,0:46:58.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在丈夫去世后
Dialogue: 1,0:46:58.72,0:47:02.29,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,对于店铺的经营又有诸多问题
Dialogue: 1,0:47:02.63,0:47:07.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,随后因为建筑疏开 到最后什么都没剩下
Dialogue: 1,0:47:09.42,0:47:12.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,因为久夫是黑村家的孩子
Dialogue: 1,0:47:13.11,0:47:15.29,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,被带到了下关市去
Dialogue: 1,0:47:16.30,0:47:18.51,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,看起来应该是答应了
Dialogue: 1,0:47:19.61,0:47:23.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,大家能够开开心心地生活着就好了
Dialogue: 1,0:47:24.15,0:47:25.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:47:34.42,0:47:36.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我去看看那些蔬菜
Dialogue: 1,0:47:50.01,0:47:51.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在我认识这些东西之前
Dialogue: 1,0:47:52.07,0:47:54.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我已经好几个月没有画过了
Dialogue: 1,0:47:55.01,0:47:57.22,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,基本都是在发呆呢
Dialogue: 1,0:48:02.07,0:48:03.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那是大和
Dialogue: 1,0:48:04.83,0:48:05.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这个是利根
Dialogue: 1,0:48:12.12,0:48:14.29,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那个 我只是…
Dialogue: 1,0:48:15.78,0:48:17.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我… 好痛
Dialogue: 1,0:48:17.29,0:48:19.93,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我只是想给住在远方的那孩子送去船的画而已
Dialogue: 1,0:48:19.93,0:48:21.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这个女人的家是这里吗
Dialogue: 1,0:48:21.72,0:48:23.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,宪…宪兵大人
Dialogue: 1,0:48:24.35,0:48:26.65,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,画了海岸线和军舰身影的写生
Dialogue: 1,0:48:27.50,0:48:28.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这是间谍行为
Dialogue: 1,0:48:28.85,0:48:30.17,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,摆出这幅的表情
Dialogue: 1,0:48:30.45,0:48:34.17,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,使人分辨不出她擅长阴险精妙的计划
Dialogue: 1,0:48:36.01,0:48:37.60,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这个女人的丈夫是
Dialogue: 1,0:48:37.91,0:48:41.21,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,海军军法会议所的下级记录员吧
Dialogue: 1,0:48:41.46,0:48:45.12,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,很有可能这女人看准时机 在别人不注意的时候泄露军事机密
Dialogue: 1,0:48:46.19,0:48:48.12,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,有没有察觉到暗号通信
Dialogue: 1,0:48:48.69,0:48:51.59,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在这女人的物品里有没有发现密码表
Dialogue: 1,0:48:51.78,0:48:53.29,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,还有透露这个女人背后关系的物品
Dialogue: 1,0:48:53.76,0:48:54.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,有没有？
Dialogue: 1,0:48:57.14,0:48:59.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这次先保留检举一事
Dialogue: 1,0:48:59.99,0:49:01.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,请时常保持雪亮的监视的眼睛
Dialogue: 1,0:49:02.10,0:49:04.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,即使是嫁进来了总归是外人
Dialogue: 1,0:49:16.39,0:49:17.47,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 1,0:49:18.60,0:49:21.82,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,怎么了 洗完的衣服一直干放在那
Dialogue: 1,0:49:22.01,0:49:23.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 周作 那是因为
Dialogue: 1,0:49:23.96,0:49:25.86,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃被宪兵抓住…
Dialogue: 1,0:49:29.07,0:49:31.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃 你过来一下
Dialogue: 1,0:49:39.23,0:49:42.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这么小的话海岸线也画不了了
Dialogue: 1,0:49:44.54,0:49:47.07,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,原来你是很喜欢画画的人呀
Dialogue: 1,0:49:47.88,0:49:50.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,下次找机会画我试试吧
Dialogue: 1,0:49:51.20,0:49:52.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 1,0:49:52.94,0:49:55.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我可能没法画得很好
Dialogue: 1,0:49:57.80,0:50:00.60,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃是间谍啊
Dialogue: 1,0:50:01.16,0:50:03.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,周作 你就好了
Dialogue: 1,0:50:04.18,0:50:07.57,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我们对着宪兵总觉得不好意思
Dialogue: 1,0:50:07.57,0:50:09.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,想笑又笑不了
Dialogue: 1,0:50:09.69,0:50:12.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,忍住的话反而会被怀疑
Dialogue: 1,0:50:15.64,0:50:17.50,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 1,0:50:17.50,0:50:20.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这孩子一旦专心入迷就注意不到周围的东西了
Dialogue: 1,0:50:20.85,0:50:22.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,看上去一副老实的样子
Dialogue: 1,0:50:22.16,0:50:24.74,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,反而又被当成是大智若愚的人
Dialogue: 1,0:50:24.75,0:50:25.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这…这个人啊
Dialogue: 1,0:50:26.17,0:50:29.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是会把「六点」回来听成「记录」的人
Dialogue: 1,0:50:29.76,0:50:31.60,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,到底会盯上什么机密啊
Dialogue: 1,0:50:31.69,0:50:33.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那群陆军的笨蛋宪兵
Dialogue: 1,0:50:33.49,0:50:36.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,虽然不是很懂 突然变得好奇怪呢
Dialogue: 1,0:50:40.46,0:50:44.06,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,大家能够开开心心地生活着就好了
Dialogue: 1,0:50:44.48,0:50:45.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:50:45.78,0:50:46.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 1,0:50:47.67,0:50:50.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,父亲呀 让父亲也听一听
Dialogue: 1,0:50:51.56,0:50:53.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就只有我笑不出来啊
Dialogue: 1,0:50:53.73,0:50:55.52,kono-text-cn-2,,0,0,0,,到底能有什么企图嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:50:55.97,0:50:58.01,kono-text-cn-2,,0,0,0,,根本什么都不懂
Dialogue: 1,0:51:00.93,0:51:04.92,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,即使是战争时期 蝉鸣蝶飞依旧
Dialogue: 1,0:50:59.82,0:51:05.20,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs50\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5\pos(337,160)\3c&H868686&}1944
Dialogue: 1,0:50:59.82,0:51:05.20,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5\pos(313,208)\3c&H868686&}年
Dialogue: 1,0:50:59.82,0:51:05.20,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs60\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5\pos(335,302)\3c&H868686&}8
Dialogue: 1,0:50:59.82,0:51:05.20,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5\pos(309,347.224)\3c&H868686&}月
Dialogue: 1,0:51:05.21,0:51:07.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好热啊
Dialogue: 1,0:51:04.45,0:51:10.96,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord0\c&HD1DFE5&\fn方正稚艺_GBK\\pos(1079.058,190.303)} 通知\n 从八月开始砂糖的配给停止\n请更加节约使用
Dialogue: 1,0:51:09.38,0:51:10.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哎呀 连砂糖也
Dialogue: 1,0:51:12.39,0:51:14.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,六月空袭骚乱的时候
Dialogue: 1,0:51:14.96,0:51:17.98,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,还以为战争已经逼近我们的身边
Dialogue: 1,0:51:18.82,0:51:20.92,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,但是现在到底是怎么样的情况呢
Dialogue: 1,0:51:24.47,0:51:25.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 1,0:51:25.94,0:51:27.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,晴美 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 1,0:51:27.93,0:51:28.94,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 1,0:51:29.59,0:51:31.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我在看蚂蚁们
Dialogue: 1,0:51:33.01,0:51:35.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,到底延伸到哪里去呢
Dialogue: 1,0:51:56.97,0:51:59.92,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,当下砂糖可是贵重物品啊
Dialogue: 1,0:52:07.00,0:52:09.84,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,把它藏在蚂蚁们找不到的地方吧
Dialogue: 1,0:52:10.27,0:52:11.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 1,0:52:12.45,0:52:13.56,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,放哪里好
Dialogue: 1,0:52:17.91,0:52:19.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:52:20.29,0:52:21.79,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我想着如果
Dialogue: 1,0:52:22.14,0:52:25.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,放在水上蚂蚁们就不会接近了
Dialogue: 1,0:52:34.27,0:52:37.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,拿去吧 去黑市买回来
Dialogue: 1,0:52:41.87,0:52:43.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,走着和平常不同的路
Dialogue: 1,0:52:46.81,0:52:48.07,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,请慢用
Dialogue: 1,0:52:53.47,0:52:55.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,按道理应该没有东西可卖才对
Dialogue: 1,0:52:56.00,0:52:57.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,为什么会有这么多人
Dialogue: 1,0:53:02.83,0:53:06.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这是台湾米 刚收成的
Dialogue: 1,0:53:02.40,0:53:07.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正毡笔黑_GBK\fs50\bord0\c&H6C6F73&\frz5.559\pos(297.058,98.303)}下次进货时间预定在月底
Dialogue: 1,0:53:07.64,0:53:10.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,或者内地米也可以拿到货哦
Dialogue: 1,0:53:12.46,0:53:15.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,田里明明是禁止种西瓜的才对
Dialogue: 1,0:53:17.31,0:53:19.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什么都有
Dialogue: 1,0:53:23.40,0:53:26.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就像是战争前的暑假一样
Dialogue: 1,0:53:27.33,0:53:29.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,砂糖一斤二十円
Dialogue: 1,0:53:29.85,0:53:32.79,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,配…配给的五十倍以上
Dialogue: 1,0:53:33.06,0:53:35.59,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,现在不买只会越来越贵
Dialogue: 1,0:53:36.03,0:53:41.30,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,母亲的私房钱加上这个月的生活费加起来才二十五円
Dialogue: 1,0:53:41.53,0:53:44.17,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,柿种
Dialogue: 1,0:53:47.45,0:53:51.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,现在砂糖变成了一百五十円左右
Dialogue: 1,0:53:51.82,0:53:54.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,一百円也买不到焦糖之类的
Dialogue: 1,0:53:55.27,0:53:59.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,买三双袜子的话差不多要一千円了
Dialogue: 1,0:54:01.13,0:54:04.65,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在这样的国家里还能活下去吗
Dialogue: 1,0:54:10.24,0:54:13.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,等下 这里到底是哪里
Dialogue: 1,0:54:13.97,0:54:15.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯？长木？
Dialogue: 1,0:54:15.88,0:54:17.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,海军墓地那儿吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:54:17.58,0:54:19.40,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 那是长迫呀
Dialogue: 1,0:54:19.52,0:54:20.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那边么？
Dialogue: 1,0:54:21.14,0:54:22.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这边才对吧
Dialogue: 1,0:54:37.94,0:54:38.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 1,0:54:43.56,0:54:44.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 1,0:54:45.22,0:54:46.06,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,西瓜
Dialogue: 1,0:54:47.73,0:54:48.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,焦糖？
Dialogue: 1,0:54:50.14,0:54:51.01,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,迷路了？
Dialogue: 1,0:54:53.04,0:54:54.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,明明是大人了？
Dialogue: 1,0:54:55.13,0:54:56.33,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你是从哪里来的
Dialogue: 1,0:54:57.04,0:54:57.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,长木
Dialogue: 1,0:54:59.02,0:55:02.56,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,大姐姐 没人能告诉我回家的路
Dialogue: 1,0:55:02.93,0:55:04.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,大家都有香香的味道
Dialogue: 1,0:55:05.14,0:55:07.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这里是龙宫城还是什么地方吗
Dialogue: 1,0:55:08.16,0:55:12.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,长木的话 在那里拐角 走到邮政局
Dialogue: 1,0:55:12.93,0:55:13.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 1,0:55:14.52,0:55:15.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,等一下下
Dialogue: 1,0:55:17.18,0:55:19.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,姐姐 问个问题
Dialogue: 1,0:55:24.86,0:55:27.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,沿着这里走 然后走出那里
Dialogue: 1,0:55:27.48,0:55:30.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在邮政局前的那个拐角往右走就是了
Dialogue: 1,0:55:31.70,0:55:33.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,非常谢谢你
Dialogue: 1,0:55:34.44,0:55:37.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这里的人其实都不是很熟悉路
Dialogue: 1,0:55:38.21,0:55:42.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,大部分都是外地人 基本没走出过这个门
Dialogue: 1,0:55:42.95,0:55:45.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你也是广岛南部的…
Dialogue: 1,0:55:46.03,0:55:46.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,海边吗
Dialogue: 1,0:55:47.36,0:55:49.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是的 你怎么知道的
Dialogue: 1,0:55:49.88,0:55:50.76,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你说的话
Dialogue: 1,0:55:52.23,0:55:53.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,江波那边吗
Dialogue: 1,0:55:53.24,0:55:55.14,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯 草津那里
Dialogue: 1,0:55:55.22,0:55:56.29,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,草津
Dialogue: 1,0:55:57.20,0:56:00.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,每年都会在奶奶家吃西瓜呢
Dialogue: 1,0:56:00.74,0:56:02.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我家里因为很穷
Dialogue: 1,0:56:03.09,0:56:05.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,只能啃别人吃剩的瓜皮
Dialogue: 1,0:56:06.39,0:56:08.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,有一次好心人给了我一个
Dialogue: 1,0:56:09.31,0:56:11.56,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,吃上了红色的部分呢
Dialogue: 1,0:56:12.35,0:56:14.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,很久远的事情了
Dialogue: 1,0:56:15.26,0:56:17.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,话说回来你画得真好呢
Dialogue: 1,0:56:17.98,0:56:21.29,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,看起来 那个…
Dialogue: 1,0:56:22.32,0:56:23.60,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,小事一桩
Dialogue: 1,0:56:24.18,0:56:26.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,另外还有什么想我画的都跟我说吧
Dialogue: 1,0:56:26.43,0:56:28.40,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,薄荷糖　蕨菜饼
Dialogue: 1,0:56:28.91,0:56:30.33,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,薄荷糖…
Dialogue: 1,0:56:30.40,0:56:34.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然后就是冰激凌 加上威化饼的
Dialogue: 1,0:56:34.88,0:56:35.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,威化？
Dialogue: 1,0:56:36.11,0:56:38.86,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不知道么？ 你没去过咖啡厅么？
Dialogue: 1,0:56:38.87,0:56:40.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,玲
Dialogue: 1,0:56:40.10,0:56:42.29,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不要再闲聊了
Dialogue: 1,0:56:42.51,0:56:44.58,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我还是要回去了
Dialogue: 1,0:56:45.21,0:56:47.74,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,下次我再给你画好了
Dialogue: 1,0:56:49.75,0:56:50.56,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 1,0:56:51.33,0:56:53.58,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这种地方还是不要来第二次
Dialogue: 1,0:56:56.99,0:56:59.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,又会再次迷路的
Dialogue: 1,0:57:20.25,0:57:21.60,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真晚啊
Dialogue: 1,0:57:21.60,0:57:25.19,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,说了去市场 我就想是不是回来的时候迷路了
Dialogue: 1,0:57:26.61,0:57:27.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 1,0:57:27.90,0:57:31.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,说到咖啡厅里带威化饼的冰激凌
Dialogue: 1,0:57:31.63,0:57:32.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你知道是什么东西么
Dialogue: 1,0:57:33.04,0:57:34.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什么 你没听过吗
Dialogue: 1,0:57:35.28,0:57:38.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那个啊 甜甜的凉凉的
Dialogue: 1,0:57:38.36,0:57:41.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,蘸上脆脆的像仙贝一样的东西吃
Dialogue: 1,0:57:42.01,0:57:43.82,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那真是…
Dialogue: 1,0:57:44.58,0:57:45.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 1,0:57:48.53,0:57:51.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,久违地说起甜食的话题
Dialogue: 1,0:57:51.11,0:57:53.96,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,喝口水都变甜了
Dialogue: 1,0:57:57.32,0:58:03.83,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs50\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5\pos(337,160)\3c&H464646&}1944
Dialogue: 1,0:57:57.32,0:58:03.83,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5\pos(313,208)\3c&H464646&}年
Dialogue: 1,0:57:57.32,0:58:03.83,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs60\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5\pos(335,302)\3c&H464646&}9
Dialogue: 1,0:57:57.32,0:58:03.83,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5\pos(309,347.224)\3c&H464646&}月
Dialogue: 1,0:58:01.25,0:58:02.50,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,天还很热
Dialogue: 1,0:58:04.32,0:58:05.84,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,北条家的媳妇
Dialogue: 1,0:58:06.32,0:58:07.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,有打给你的电话
Dialogue: 1,0:58:09.13,0:58:11.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,来了 给我的电话吗
Dialogue: 1,0:58:15.03,0:58:16.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 这个这个
Dialogue: 1,0:58:17.77,0:58:19.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 1,0:58:19.37,0:58:21.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,受到蒙羞的人是周作
Dialogue: 1,0:58:21.10,0:58:22.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你啊 就这个样子出门…
Dialogue: 1,0:58:32.66,0:58:35.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就在附近 稍微走一走吧
Dialogue: 1,0:58:35.59,0:58:38.74,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然后 GKF的情况如何
Dialogue: 1,0:58:35.59,0:58:38.74,kono-text-cn - tips,,0,0,0,,注: GKF指南西方面艦隊
Dialogue: 1,0:58:38.98,0:58:40.19,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,现在是很空闲的样子
Dialogue: 1,0:58:40.19,0:58:41.07,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 1,0:58:41.28,0:58:42.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嘛 先去喝点冰啤酒吧
Dialogue: 1,0:58:59.54,0:59:02.57,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,周作 我给你送笔记本来了
Dialogue: 1,0:59:08.52,0:59:09.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 1,0:59:10.22,0:59:12.12,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,涂得好白啊 没问题吧
Dialogue: 1,0:59:13.23,0:59:14.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,会不会很奇怪呀
Dialogue: 1,0:59:16.00,0:59:17.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,没事 精神就好
Dialogue: 1,0:59:18.59,0:59:19.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 1,0:59:21.57,0:59:22.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,工作怎么办
Dialogue: 1,0:59:22.97,0:59:26.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,明明不是很急 却特意帮我把笔记本拿过来
Dialogue: 1,0:59:27.28,0:59:30.14,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你说过到镇上买东西很开心对吧
Dialogue: 1,0:59:34.40,0:59:35.17,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:59:35.86,0:59:36.94,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,果然身体有什么…
Dialogue: 1,0:59:37.28,0:59:39.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在偷偷乐而已啦
Dialogue: 1,0:59:45.23,0:59:47.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,本来还想着看电影
Dialogue: 1,0:59:49.63,0:59:52.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,刚好有艘大船回港了
Dialogue: 1,0:59:54.76,0:59:56.40,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,没办法 只能让给他们看了
Dialogue: 1,0:59:57.32,0:59:59.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,虽然有点可惜 还是等下一次吧
Dialogue: 1,1:00:02.81,1:00:03.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃？
Dialogue: 1,1:00:04.34,1:00:09.01,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,小学同年级的有成为水兵的
Dialogue: 1,1:00:09.58,1:00:11.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,见到了不知道要怎么办好…
Dialogue: 1,1:00:12.15,1:00:14.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,普通地打招呼不就行了
Dialogue: 1,1:00:15.58,1:00:18.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,如果现在跟以前认识的人见了面的话
Dialogue: 1,1:00:18.35,1:00:22.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我会不会就从梦里醒来了呢
Dialogue: 1,1:00:22.66,1:00:23.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,梦…
Dialogue: 1,1:00:23.86,1:00:27.76,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,住所跟姓氏都变了 净是让人为难的事
Dialogue: 1,1:00:28.01,1:00:31.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不过即使如此 能有周作对我好
Dialogue: 1,1:00:31.26,1:00:33.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,而且还交到了朋友
Dialogue: 1,1:00:33.83,1:00:36.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯… 现在醒来的话就不有趣了
Dialogue: 1,1:00:37.45,1:00:40.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,如果现在的我就是真正的我 那就挺好的
Dialogue: 1,1:00:40.37,1:00:41.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 1,1:00:42.91,1:00:45.47,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,过去的事 没选择的道路
Dialogue: 1,1:00:46.16,1:00:49.01,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,都跟醒来时结束的梦没两样
Dialogue: 1,1:00:49.71,1:00:52.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃 选择了你
Dialogue: 1,1:00:52.61,1:00:55.07,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,对我来说很可能是最好的选择了
Dialogue: 1,1:00:57.00,1:00:59.94,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,只不过你好像有点瘦了 真让人担心
Dialogue: 1,1:01:00.58,1:01:04.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,说起来 最近好像没什么胃口…
Dialogue: 1,1:01:11.50,1:01:13.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,给 2人份
Dialogue: 1,1:01:20.38,1:01:22.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,毕竟早上白白地多吃了那么多
Dialogue: 1,1:01:22.81,1:01:24.76,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,大概这个量应该够了吧
Dialogue: 1,1:01:26.79,1:01:28.58,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,果然还是一人的分量
Dialogue: 1,1:01:28.99,1:01:35.56,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1447,834)\fs50\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(331,360)}1944
Dialogue: 1,1:01:28.99,1:01:35.56,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1447,834)\fs70\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(303,410)}年
Dialogue: 1,1:01:28.99,1:01:35.56,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1447,834)\fs60\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(331,508.542)}12
Dialogue: 1,1:01:28.99,1:01:35.56,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1447,834)\fs70\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(303,549.224)}月
Dialogue: 1,1:01:28.83,1:01:35.40,kono-text-cn - tips,,0,0,0,,注：日本海军自卫队 红表示减速 黑表示加速
Dialogue: 1,1:01:28.83,1:01:32.82,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,准备入港 前进低速 红20
Dialogue: 1,1:01:33.08,1:01:35.40,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,航向不变 低速整定 红20
Dialogue: 1,1:01:35.40,1:01:37.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,航向不变
Dialogue: 1,1:01:39.38,1:01:41.28,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,之后我会帮你试着拜托他的
Dialogue: 1,1:01:43.49,1:01:44.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 1,1:01:45.02,1:01:47.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是真正的水兵
Dialogue: 1,1:01:49.38,1:01:52.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在井口那边突然遇见的
Dialogue: 1,1:01:52.70,1:01:53.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我是水原哲
Dialogue: 1,1:01:54.25,1:01:55.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,军舰青叶的船员
Dialogue: 1,1:01:56.68,1:01:58.91,kono-text-cn - tips,,0,0,0,,注：甲型巡洋舰 或 一等巡洋舰
Dialogue: 1,1:01:56.68,1:01:58.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,青叶的话是甲巡吧
Dialogue: 1,1:01:59.66,1:02:01.51,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,喂 晴美
Dialogue: 1,1:02:04.97,1:02:07.50,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,冬天也还晒得那么黑
Dialogue: 1,1:02:07.65,1:02:11.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那么 你是来我们家泡澡的吗
Dialogue: 1,1:02:11.32,1:02:14.21,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯 现在是叫做泡澡登陆的自由时间
Dialogue: 1,1:02:14.69,1:02:16.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,也没什么想去的地方
Dialogue: 1,1:02:16.87,1:02:19.57,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,所以就依靠了同乡的铃 来这里打扰了
Dialogue: 1,1:02:20.16,1:02:22.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,谢谢各位对铃的照顾
Dialogue: 1,1:02:23.89,1:02:27.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃从以前除了画画跟制作干海苔就没什么优点
Dialogue: 1,1:02:27.84,1:02:30.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,现在也只是个呆瓜吧
Dialogue: 1,1:02:30.56,1:02:32.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,如果大家不客气地跟我讲的话
Dialogue: 1,1:02:32.99,1:02:34.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我就把她带回去了
Dialogue: 1,1:02:39.24,1:02:41.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要装腔作势也得有个限度
Dialogue: 1,1:02:41.31,1:02:43.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,还「铃 铃」地直呼名字
Dialogue: 1,1:02:44.78,1:02:46.33,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那要怎么称呼才好
Dialogue: 1,1:02:46.66,1:02:48.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你不都已经不是浦野了么
Dialogue: 1,1:02:49.83,1:02:52.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃 不能对水兵这么粗鲁
Dialogue: 1,1:03:02.49,1:03:03.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,有什么好笑的吗
Dialogue: 1,1:03:04.02,1:03:07.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好笑啊 你真是普通啊
Dialogue: 1,1:03:07.84,1:03:09.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好吃 嗯 好吃
Dialogue: 1,1:03:09.89,1:03:11.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,粗茶淡饭而已
Dialogue: 1,1:03:11.43,1:03:13.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真是惬意
Dialogue: 1,1:03:13.77,1:03:15.92,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,喂 铃也进来吧
Dialogue: 1,1:03:16.16,1:03:17.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你傻吗
Dialogue: 1,1:03:17.58,1:03:19.82,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃 煤油灯在哪
Dialogue: 1,1:03:20.42,1:03:22.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好像是在防空壕里面
Dialogue: 1,1:03:22.90,1:03:23.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 1,1:03:25.16,1:03:27.79,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,晴美将来也要成为水兵
Dialogue: 1,1:03:28.41,1:03:30.01,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那样太好了
Dialogue: 1,1:03:30.01,1:03:30.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 1,1:03:31.36,1:03:32.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那就不客气了
Dialogue: 1,1:03:32.90,1:03:33.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,招呼呢
Dialogue: 1,1:03:34.19,1:03:35.56,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 1,1:03:36.46,1:03:37.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 1,1:03:40.05,1:03:41.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,陆地上就是好
Dialogue: 1,1:03:41.86,1:03:43.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那么我就
Dialogue: 1,1:03:44.36,1:03:46.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,青叶怎么样了
Dialogue: 1,1:03:47.12,1:03:50.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在马尼拉负伤 历尽艰辛终于回来了
Dialogue: 1,1:03:50.83,1:03:55.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,明明是一艘好舰 却又要远离战场默默无闻了
Dialogue: 1,1:03:57.23,1:03:58.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我说周作啊
Dialogue: 1,1:03:59.09,1:04:02.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,苟且偷生真是让人焦躁
Dialogue: 1,1:04:04.74,1:04:05.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,水原
Dialogue: 1,1:04:06.19,1:04:10.01,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,因为父亲有夜勤不回来 今晚我就是家主
Dialogue: 1,1:04:10.56,1:04:14.14,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,虽然对不起你 但是我不能让你在这里过夜
Dialogue: 1,1:04:18.79,1:04:19.33,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 1,1:04:19.82,1:04:21.74,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,让他睡农具房2楼了
Dialogue: 1,1:04:22.56,1:04:24.21,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真是稀奇
Dialogue: 1,1:04:24.51,1:04:26.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你也有这么强势的时候
Dialogue: 1,1:04:28.69,1:04:29.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 1,1:04:29.58,1:04:32.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,脚炉开了 给他带去吧
Dialogue: 1,1:04:32.41,1:04:34.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然后慢慢跟他聊天吧
Dialogue: 1,1:04:34.55,1:04:36.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,也许再也见不到了
Dialogue: 1,1:04:51.41,1:04:53.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,对不起 让你在这里睡
Dialogue: 1,1:04:54.66,1:04:56.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,跟吊床比算是特别舒服了
Dialogue: 1,1:04:57.43,1:04:59.30,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,诶 有很多要聊的吧
Dialogue: 1,1:05:00.02,1:05:01.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,天很冷 脚先放进去吧
Dialogue: 1,1:05:06.19,1:05:08.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,给你 是礼物
Dialogue: 1,1:05:08.94,1:05:09.65,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 1,1:05:12.70,1:05:13.79,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要做成羽毛笔吗
Dialogue: 1,1:05:16.22,1:05:16.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 1,1:05:25.65,1:05:27.16,kono-text-cn-2,,0,0,0,,写得出来啊
Dialogue: 1,1:05:25.29,1:05:27.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,写得出写得出
Dialogue: 1,1:05:28.16,1:05:29.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,虽然看着像鹭的羽毛
Dialogue: 1,1:05:29.95,1:05:32.58,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然而毕竟当时见到的时候是在南部的海上
Dialogue: 1,1:05:32.70,1:05:35.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鹭会渡海吗
Dialogue: 1,1:05:35.48,1:05:36.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 1,1:05:36.96,1:05:40.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,毕竟在江波那边可是一整年都只在河上面站着
Dialogue: 1,1:05:42.04,1:05:44.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,以前在江波真的很多
Dialogue: 1,1:05:45.58,1:05:46.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,总觉得不太行
Dialogue: 1,1:05:46.93,1:05:48.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,没法按想象中的来画
Dialogue: 1,1:05:49.28,1:05:51.01,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你也有这种时候的吗
Dialogue: 1,1:05:52.57,1:05:53.56,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,难不成
Dialogue: 1,1:05:54.22,1:05:55.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,很久没画了吗
Dialogue: 1,1:05:56.16,1:05:57.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,算是吧…
Dialogue: 1,1:05:59.07,1:06:00.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那幅画
Dialogue: 1,1:06:00.76,1:06:02.43,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那些波浪的白兔
Dialogue: 1,1:06:03.82,1:06:04.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 1,1:06:05.58,1:06:07.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,毕竟那之后真是不得了了
Dialogue: 1,1:06:09.27,1:06:10.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 1,1:06:11.28,1:06:12.86,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你忘了吗？
Dialogue: 1,1:06:13.28,1:06:16.71,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,老师把那幅画放到广岛市的比赛里参赛
Dialogue: 1,1:06:17.15,1:06:19.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然后好评如潮
Dialogue: 1,1:06:20.06,1:06:21.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我当时真的很为难
Dialogue: 1,1:06:22.64,1:06:25.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,毕竟大家都认为是我画的
Dialogue: 1,1:06:25.73,1:06:27.43,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真正的功劳
Dialogue: 1,1:06:27.61,1:06:28.92,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,明明是你
Dialogue: 1,1:06:38.28,1:06:40.29,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃真暖
Dialogue: 1,1:06:40.73,1:06:42.71,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃真柔弱
Dialogue: 1,1:06:42.84,1:06:44.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真香
Dialogue: 1,1:06:48.16,1:06:49.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,水原
Dialogue: 1,1:06:50.97,1:06:54.11,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我感觉自己一直在等着这样的日子
Dialogue: 1,1:06:55.39,1:06:57.60,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你能这样过来
Dialogue: 1,1:06:58.59,1:07:00.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,明明距离自己那么近
Dialogue: 1,1:07:01.17,1:07:02.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 1,1:07:04.03,1:07:07.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我真的 被那个人给气死了
Dialogue: 1,1:07:08.81,1:07:09.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 1,1:07:10.08,1:07:11.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真的对不起
Dialogue: 1,1:07:12.91,1:07:16.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你…喜欢那个人吧
Dialogue: 1,1:07:16.92,1:07:17.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,1:07:20.05,1:07:22.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真是普通得让人吃惊
Dialogue: 1,1:07:22.57,1:07:23.30,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 1,1:07:23.41,1:07:25.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,简直像为理所当然的事情生气
Dialogue: 1,1:07:26.10,1:07:28.40,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,为理所当然的事情道着歉一样
Dialogue: 1,1:07:29.15,1:07:31.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不带你回去真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 1,1:07:31.61,1:07:34.52,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不是因为被迫嫁给别人而觉得为难吗
Dialogue: 1,1:07:36.42,1:07:37.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 1,1:07:40.14,1:07:41.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,大4年是吧
Dialogue: 1,1:07:42.64,1:07:43.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你说周作？
Dialogue: 1,1:07:44.06,1:07:46.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,跟死去的哥哥同岁
Dialogue: 1,1:07:47.68,1:07:49.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,因为我家比较穷
Dialogue: 1,1:07:49.34,1:07:52.33,kono-text-cn - tips,,0,0,0,,注：旧大日本帝国海军培养海军军官的军事学校
Dialogue: 1,1:07:49.34,1:07:52.33,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哥哥进了免费的海军兵学校
Dialogue: 1,1:07:53.14,1:07:56.11,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,因为哥哥死了 我也进了海军
Dialogue: 1,1:07:57.01,1:07:58.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,明明全都是理所当然的
Dialogue: 1,1:07:59.21,1:08:03.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我也许是哪个地方跟人类的理所当然相背离了
Dialogue: 1,1:08:04.68,1:08:05.51,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 1,1:08:06.47,1:08:09.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在这里看到铃这么普通 我放心了
Dialogue: 1,1:08:09.91,1:08:12.64,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我可不想被别人叫做英灵
Dialogue: 1,1:08:13.34,1:08:16.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,如果要想起我 就笑着想起我吧
Dialogue: 1,1:08:17.59,1:08:18.98,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,只有你
Dialogue: 1,1:08:19.35,1:08:23.53,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要在这个世界一直地普通下去正常下去
Dialogue: 1,1:08:24.00,1:08:24.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 1,1:08:25.55,1:08:27.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你变漂亮了
Dialogue: 1,1:08:27.84,1:08:29.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你傻吗
Dialogue: 1,1:08:31.89,1:08:35.51,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真的从小就开始
Dialogue: 1,1:08:35.73,1:08:38.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,对你有着没法说出重要话的毛病啊
Dialogue: 1,1:08:32.71,1:08:39.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(941,0)\fn@方正毡笔黑_gbk\fs60\frz253.4\bord0\c&H85645B&\move(466.877,173.175,579.471,205.598,0,3485)}哲
Dialogue: 1,1:08:32.71,1:08:39.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(941,0)\fn@方正毡笔黑_GBK\fs60\frz253.4\bord0\c&H85645B&\move(384.095,261.289,499.36,293.721,0,3485))}羽毛谢谢了
Dialogue: 1,1:08:32.71,1:08:39.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(941,0)\fn@方正毡笔黑_GBK\fs60\frz253.4\bord0\c&H85645B&\move(301.314,349.401,419.249,384.494,0,3485)}谢谢你变得那么优秀
Dialogue: 1,1:08:32.71,1:08:39.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(941,0)\fn@方正毡笔黑_GBK\fs60\frz253.4\bord0\c&H85645B&\move(237.224,360.082,360.5,392.505,0,3485)}很高兴你能活着来看我
Dialogue: 1,1:08:32.71,1:08:39.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(941,0)\fn@方正毡笔黑_GBK\fs60\frz253.4\bord0\c&H85645B&\move(117.058,573.691,243.004,608.784,0,3485)}铃
Dialogue: 1,1:08:49.83,1:08:51.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 鬼哥
Dialogue: 1,1:08:52.31,1:08:55.92,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,但是用那样一颗石子来代替尸骨
Dialogue: 1,1:08:56.66,1:08:58.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,因为太过小了 小澄竟然…
Dialogue: 1,1:08:58.64,1:09:01.21,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鬼哥的…脑子？
Dialogue: 1,1:09:01.95,1:09:03.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,…这样搞混了
Dialogue: 1,1:09:04.00,1:09:05.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你哥哥是怎样的人
Dialogue: 1,1:09:06.73,1:09:09.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,大冷天的被叫过来 真傻
Dialogue: 1,1:09:09.56,1:09:12.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那个要一真的会这么容易死掉吗
Dialogue: 1,1:09:13.36,1:09:15.56,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真没劲 人总是突然消失了
Dialogue: 1,1:09:16.20,1:09:21.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,看不见身影了 就…没法传达话语了
Dialogue: 1,1:09:23.04,1:09:24.28,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,周作
Dialogue: 1,1:09:25.57,1:09:28.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,前段时间 谢谢你了
Dialogue: 1,1:09:30.23,1:09:33.53,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,给我时间和水原说话
Dialogue: 1,1:09:34.76,1:09:35.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,没…
Dialogue: 1,1:09:36.36,1:09:37.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不过 周作
Dialogue: 1,1:09:38.44,1:09:40.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,夫妇是那样的吗
Dialogue: 1,1:09:42.07,1:09:45.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,因为是我硬要让你嫁过来
Dialogue: 1,1:09:47.28,1:09:49.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,但你明明不表现给我看
Dialogue: 1,1:09:49.51,1:09:50.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那样的生气表情
Dialogue: 1,1:09:51.15,1:09:51.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 1,1:09:52.33,1:09:54.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,现在不就在表现给你看吗
Dialogue: 1,1:09:55.88,1:09:58.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嚯~ 我倒是不知道你会生气
Dialogue: 1,1:09:58.70,1:10:00.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那是你注意力涣散而已
Dialogue: 1,1:10:01.02,1:10:02.14,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嚯~
Dialogue: 1,1:10:03.92,1:10:07.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,所以你今天才穿了破洞的袜子
Dialogue: 1,1:10:07.59,1:10:11.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是因为铃昨晚补的袜子我的脚穿不进去了
Dialogue: 1,1:10:11.13,1:10:12.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,也有别的袜子吧
Dialogue: 1,1:10:12.65,1:10:16.53,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,两位 这架必须得现在吵吗
Dialogue: 1,1:10:17.87,1:10:20.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,又走错路了 是这边
Dialogue: 1,1:10:20.48,1:10:21.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 1,1:10:22.18,1:10:25.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我们家在那边 在那座灰之峰的方向
Dialogue: 1,1:10:25.55,1:10:26.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,都说了我知道
Dialogue: 1,1:10:30.48,1:10:33.86,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那个冬天 雪很多
Dialogue: 1,1:10:34.65,1:10:36.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真让人期盼春天的到来
Dialogue: 1,1:10:37.87,1:10:43.38,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1447,834)\fs50\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(331,160)}1945
