Dialogue: 1,1:15:08.53,1:15:10.57,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真是提不起劲
Dialogue: 1,1:15:10.76,1:15:13.28,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,毕竟那人她丈夫都已经战死了
Dialogue: 1,1:15:13.34,1:15:16.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这次连17岁的儿子也死了
Dialogue: 1,1:15:16.21,1:15:18.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,恭喜你了
Dialogue: 1,1:15:22.89,1:15:24.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,防空服装准备好
Dialogue: 1,1:15:24.46,1:15:25.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,火源处理没问题
Dialogue: 1,1:15:25.62,1:15:27.17,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,门窗和拉门拆掉
Dialogue: 1,1:15:27.33,1:15:28.40,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,防空用具
Dialogue: 1,1:15:28.41,1:15:29.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 1,1:15:29.56,1:15:32.11,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真是的 太暗了都看不见了
Dialogue: 1,1:15:32.11,1:15:32.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 1,1:15:33.99,1:15:35.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 1,1:15:35.89,1:15:37.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哪里来的猫？
Dialogue: 1,1:15:43.20,1:15:45.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,警报已经听腻了
Dialogue: 1,1:15:59.71,1:16:01.12,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,第一次见到
Dialogue: 1,1:16:07.54,1:16:12.88,kono-text-cn - tips,,0,0,0,,此为F-13超级堡垒拍摄到大和号出击照片
