Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.76,1:35:15.48,kono-zs,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&HFFFFFF&\bord3\1a&H64&\an5\pos(548.163,760.536)}m 0 0 l 0 500 l 400 500 l 400 0\N
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.76,1:35:15.48,kono-zs,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&HFFFFFF&\bord3\1a&H64&\an5\pos(649.726,255.207)}m 0 0 l 0 300 l 200 300 l 200 0\N
Dialogue: 1,1:35:13.55,1:35:15.60,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真惨啊
Dialogue: 1,1:35:26.88,1:35:30.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,吴市也遭受了好几次空袭 真是可怜
Dialogue: 1,1:35:32.02,1:35:36.45,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,而且你也做不了家务了 以后会更加辛苦吧
Dialogue: 1,1:35:38.68,1:35:40.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我说 铃
Dialogue: 1,1:35:41.06,1:35:43.65,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,回来广岛吧
Dialogue: 1,1:35:44.88,1:35:46.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,没有严重的空袭
Dialogue: 1,1:35:47.13,1:35:49.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鬼哥哥也已经不在了
Dialogue: 1,1:35:49.22,1:35:51.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,已经没有会欺负我们的人了
Dialogue: 1,1:35:53.99,1:35:55.82,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,也不是这样
Dialogue: 1,1:35:56.92,1:36:00.71,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我要看下你的将校先生是不是美男子再决定
Dialogue: 1,1:36:00.77,1:36:03.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,讨厌 真是不纯
Dialogue: 1,1:36:03.19,1:36:04.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,开玩笑开玩笑啦
Dialogue: 1,1:36:04.44,1:36:05.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那再见啦
Dialogue: 1,1:36:05.73,1:36:06.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,扭曲了
Dialogue: 1,1:36:06.88,1:36:09.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我倒是觉得是个不错的想法
Dialogue: 1,1:36:09.95,1:36:12.96,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,下个月的六号是江波的祭典呢
Dialogue: 1,1:36:13.01,1:36:14.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,早点回来吧
Dialogue: 1,1:36:14.90,1:36:17.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 澄
Dialogue: 1,1:36:17.32,1:36:20.19,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我觉得鬼哥哥死了真是太好了
Dialogue: 1,1:36:21.14,1:36:22.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,扭曲了的是我
Dialogue: 1,1:36:23.60,1:36:25.82,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就像用左手画出来的画一样
Dialogue: 1,1:37:13.43,1:37:15.92,kono-text-cn-2,,0,0,0,,哎 今天也来了
Dialogue: 1,1:37:14.83,1:37:18.64,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好像又要很久的样子 把身边的东西带上吧
Dialogue: 1,1:37:18.65,1:37:18.79,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,1:37:18.80,1:37:19.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好烫
Dialogue: 1,1:37:19.48,1:37:22.05,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃 你先去吧
Dialogue: 1,1:37:29.82,1:37:31.07,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不能过来
Dialogue: 1,1:37:32.64,1:37:34.94,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,现在 不能过来这边
Dialogue: 1,1:37:45.26,1:37:46.53,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就是那边
Dialogue: 1,1:37:46.60,1:37:48.30,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,往那边一直逃
Dialogue: 1,1:37:48.75,1:37:51.45,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,越过了山 就是广岛了
Dialogue: 1,1:38:24.09,1:38:25.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你想死吗
Dialogue: 1,1:38:26.38,1:38:28.52,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,对不起 鹭鸶…
Dialogue: 1,1:38:28.88,1:38:30.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,有只鹭鸶飞过
Dialogue: 1,1:38:31.02,1:38:33.79,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯 应该是从海边逃过来的吧
Dialogue: 1,1:38:34.97,1:38:37.21,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,周作 我
Dialogue: 1,1:38:38.13,1:38:39.59,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要回广岛去
Dialogue: 1,1:38:44.25,1:38:45.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你不想再回来了吗
Dialogue: 1,1:38:47.40,1:38:48.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是在意手的事吗
Dialogue: 1,1:38:50.22,1:38:51.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是空袭很可怕吗
Dialogue: 1,1:38:52.05,1:38:53.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,还是因为晴美吗
Dialogue: 1,1:38:53.76,1:38:56.01,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,对 对
Dialogue: 1,1:38:56.74,1:38:57.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,全部都对
Dialogue: 1,1:38:58.06,1:38:59.12,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我听不到
Dialogue: 1,1:38:59.19,1:39:00.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 1,1:39:01.80,1:39:03.22,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那为什么
Dialogue: 1,1:39:04.97,1:39:08.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃 我很幸福
Dialogue: 1,1:39:08.54,1:39:11.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这一年半 能回到有你在的家
Dialogue: 1,1:39:12.27,1:39:14.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,无论是和你牵手散步
Dialogue: 1,1:39:14.42,1:39:15.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,还是和你聊天
Dialogue: 1,1:39:17.63,1:39:19.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,难道你就不是吗
Dialogue: 1,1:39:19.40,1:39:21.43,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我家还是这么陌生吗
Dialogue: 1,1:39:24.63,1:39:25.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我听不到
Dialogue: 1,1:39:26.94,1:39:28.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,听不到 听不到
Dialogue: 1,1:39:28.29,1:39:29.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,一句都听不到
Dialogue: 1,1:39:29.61,1:39:31.21,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,回去 回去
Dialogue: 1,1:39:31.22,1:39:33.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我要回广岛去
Dialogue: 1,1:39:33.13,1:39:34.43,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊是吗
Dialogue: 1,1:39:35.35,1:39:36.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,随便你
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.67,1:39:54.13,kono-hmz,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1523,1043)\frz270\pos(293.352,291.175)\c&HE7E7E6&}九天后
Dialogue: 1,1:39:49.92,1:39:52.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,中国军管区内上空没有敌机
Dialogue: 1,1:39:53.34,1:39:56.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,中国军管区内上空没有敌机
Dialogue: 1,1:39:56.74,1:40:02.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,广岛地区7时31分警戒警报已解除
Dialogue: 1,1:40:03.68,1:40:06.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在正好的时间解除了
Dialogue: 1,1:40:06.14,1:40:07.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那我就先走了
Dialogue: 1,1:40:07.94,1:40:10.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯 路上小心
Dialogue: 1,1:40:11.21,1:40:13.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 1,1:40:14.20,1:40:15.64,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 1,1:40:16.10,1:40:19.12,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真是的 一大早就这么热
Dialogue: 1,1:40:21.20,1:40:22.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,会很寂寞呢
Dialogue: 1,1:40:23.41,1:40:25.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,如果铃不在了的话
Dialogue: 1,1:40:45.63,1:40:47.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,所以 是几点
Dialogue: 1,1:40:49.26,1:40:50.22,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,医院
Dialogue: 1,1:40:50.92,1:40:53.45,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 10点左右
Dialogue: 1,1:40:57.44,1:40:58.76,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你这个打扮不行
Dialogue: 1,1:41:10.43,1:41:12.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不好意思 那个…
Dialogue: 1,1:41:13.90,1:41:16.51,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 这个不是要洗的
Dialogue: 1,1:41:18.52,1:41:21.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是今天吧 你家那边的祭典
Dialogue: 1,1:41:22.92,1:41:23.45,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 1,1:41:24.18,1:41:26.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我是打算周末回去的
Dialogue: 1,1:41:26.78,1:41:29.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不过医院的预约只有今天能拿到
Dialogue: 1,1:41:33.83,1:41:35.11,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,别偷看啊
Dialogue: 1,1:41:35.12,1:41:36.12,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 1,1:41:37.64,1:41:39.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,反正去了也约不到
Dialogue: 1,1:41:40.25,1:41:42.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,医生也是很忙的
Dialogue: 1,1:41:43.05,1:41:46.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,还要让广岛的医院写介绍信才行
Dialogue: 1,1:41:47.72,1:41:50.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,再说了 汽车的车票也买不到
Dialogue: 1,1:41:53.94,1:41:57.12,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你妹妹纯棉那件给你改成裤子了
Dialogue: 1,1:41:57.95,1:42:00.19,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,橡皮筋也给你缝上了 你自己穿起来吧
Dialogue: 1,1:42:00.56,1:42:02.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,橡皮筋是拼凑起来的抱歉了
Dialogue: 1,1:42:03.52,1:42:06.21,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,谢…谢谢
Dialogue: 1,1:42:10.28,1:42:11.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 1,1:42:11.90,1:42:14.57,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,把晴美的死怪在你身上
Dialogue: 1,1:42:15.90,1:42:16.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 1,1:42:18.87,1:42:21.42,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我喜欢的人很早就死了
Dialogue: 1,1:42:22.18,1:42:24.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,店也为了防火带给拆了
Dialogue: 1,1:42:25.27,1:42:27.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,孩子也再也见不到了
Dialogue: 1,1:42:28.24,1:42:31.12,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不过这也是自己所选择的道路的结果
Dialogue: 1,1:42:33.09,1:42:34.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在这点上
Dialogue: 1,1:42:34.79,1:42:37.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你顺从周围的人嫁到了一个陌生的家里
Dialogue: 1,1:42:37.73,1:42:39.74,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,百依百顺地干活
Dialogue: 1,1:42:41.14,1:42:43.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我认为那一定是很无趣的人生吧
Dialogue: 1,1:42:48.66,1:42:51.17,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃的归宿是这里也行
Dialogue: 1,1:42:51.39,1:42:52.43,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是哪里都行
Dialogue: 1,1:42:53.08,1:42:55.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不要有太多顾虑 自己决定吧
Dialogue: 1,1:43:07.59,1:43:10.60,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,径子 刚刚是不是哪里发光了
Dialogue: 1,1:43:10.61,1:43:12.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,1:43:12.62,1:43:15.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是打雷吧 明明天气这么好
Dialogue: 1,1:43:15.77,1:43:18.19,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那个 这个还是…
Dialogue: 1,1:43:18.41,1:43:20.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,能帮我洗吗
Dialogue: 1,1:43:21.20,1:43:23.79,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,还有就是…
Dialogue: 1,1:43:24.39,1:43:26.74,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,能让我待在这里吗
Dialogue: 1,1:43:26.80,1:43:27.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊我知道了
Dialogue: 1,1:43:27.49,1:43:30.53,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我知道了别靠过来 很热的
Dialogue: 1,1:43:40.09,1:43:41.74,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,刚刚是怎么回事
Dialogue: 1,1:43:44.37,1:43:47.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不好 JOFK什么都听不到
Dialogue: 1,1:43:47.17,1:43:48.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,情况呢
Dialogue: 1,1:43:48.62,1:43:49.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 1,1:43:50.81,1:43:52.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,来这边看下
Dialogue: 1,1:43:56.41,1:43:59.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那朵云是怎么回事
Dialogue: 1,1:44:00.37,1:44:01.06,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,云？
Dialogue: 1,1:44:02.28,1:44:05.79,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那朵云很大吧 叫「砧状积雨云」哦
Dialogue: 1,1:44:06.40,1:44:08.22,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这里是冈山放送局
Dialogue: 1,1:44:08.46,1:44:11.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,广岛放送局？广岛放送局？
Dialogue: 1,1:44:11.78,1:44:13.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这里是冈山放送局
Dialogue: 1,1:44:13.69,1:44:18.86,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我以为掉了什么下来 原来是广岛的传阅板
Dialogue: 1,1:44:26.03,1:44:29.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,有空闲的人等下到邻保馆集合
Dialogue: 1,1:44:26.03,1:44:29.75,kono-text-cn - tips,,0,0,0,,注：邻保馆：在有贫困，教育，歧视和环境等比较恶劣的问题的区域，拥有解决这些问题的专门知识的人常驻，\n对当地人进行适当的援助的社会福利设施。
Dialogue: 1,1:44:31.47,1:44:33.93,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,知多你是护士啊
Dialogue: 1,1:44:33.94,1:44:36.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是 草鞋什么的我也没做过
Dialogue: 1,1:44:37.44,1:44:39.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这附近的人都是这样
Dialogue: 1,1:44:39.71,1:44:41.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这样就可以了吗
Dialogue: 1,1:44:41.04,1:44:41.57,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,1:44:43.41,1:44:45.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,单手没法做的很好
Dialogue: 1,1:44:45.84,1:44:47.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你是在挖苦我吗
Dialogue: 1,1:44:47.84,1:44:50.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然后这些草鞋要做什么的
Dialogue: 1,1:44:50.46,1:44:51.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,送去广岛
Dialogue: 1,1:44:51.86,1:44:54.53,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要是和上个月的空袭一样道路都融了的话
Dialogue: 1,1:44:54.58,1:44:56.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鞋子和木屐就不能用了
Dialogue: 1,1:44:57.26,1:44:58.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我能跟过去吗
Dialogue: 1,1:44:59.08,1:45:00.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,受伤的人不行
Dialogue: 1,1:45:00.39,1:45:03.59,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我儿子也给广岛的兵队征召了
Dialogue: 1,1:45:03.82,1:45:06.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这样的话要不要乘明天的卡车去
Dialogue: 1,1:45:06.38,1:45:09.42,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,吴市的空袭广岛也经常帮助我们
Dialogue: 1,1:45:09.54,1:45:11.28,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,算是报答
Dialogue: 1,1:45:14.40,1:45:15.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这样扎头发的时间也省下来了
Dialogue: 1,1:45:16.29,1:45:18.05,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我不会给你们添麻烦的
Dialogue: 1,1:45:18.15,1:45:18.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 1,1:45:19.81,1:45:20.98,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,又来 笨蛋
Dialogue: 1,1:45:20.98,1:45:23.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,快点回家剪整齐点
Dialogue: 1,1:45:23.62,1:45:26.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我家人也说近期要到广岛去
Dialogue: 1,1:45:27.69,1:45:30.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好像是新型的炸弹落在了广岛
Dialogue: 1,1:45:32.21,1:45:33.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃家里没事吧
Dialogue: 1,1:45:33.79,1:45:34.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 1,1:45:36.16,1:45:39.96,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,镇守府也派了救援
Dialogue: 1,1:45:50.04,1:45:52.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你也是从广岛来的吗
Dialogue: 1,1:46:07.69,1:46:10.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就这么坐着死去的吗
Dialogue: 1,1:46:10.52,1:46:13.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,从广岛走到这边来
Dialogue: 1,1:46:13.00,1:46:15.98,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哎 是哪里的谁也不知道
Dialogue: 1,1:46:16.13,1:46:18.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,样子和衣服也都破破烂烂了
Dialogue: 1,1:46:18.33,1:46:20.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不要和北条家的妻子说起
Dialogue: 1,1:46:20.63,1:46:24.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那个孩子的脸都看不清了 真可怜
Dialogue: 1,1:46:27.12,1:46:29.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我摘了桉树的叶子过来了
Dialogue: 1,1:46:29.73,1:46:31.47,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,请用来做蚊香
Dialogue: 1,1:46:32.65,1:46:33.96,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 1,1:46:34.58,1:46:36.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要坚持下去哦
Dialogue: 1,1:46:36.38,1:46:36.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,1:46:37.19,1:46:37.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 1,1:46:38.53,1:46:41.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,江波的浦野十郎 喜乃 澄
Dialogue: 1,1:46:42.91,1:46:46.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,草津的森田丝糸 麻里奈 千鹤子
Dialogue: 1,1:46:48.35,1:46:50.14,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我也想变得坚强
Dialogue: 1,1:46:51.11,1:46:52.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,想要变得温柔和顽强
Dialogue: 1,1:46:53.34,1:46:54.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就像这座镇子上的人一样
Dialogue: 1,1:46:55.80,1:46:57.65,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 好吵啊
Dialogue: 1,1:46:57.89,1:47:00.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我是不会屈服于这样的暴力的
Dialogue: 1,1:47:00.89,1:47:03.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正中等线_GBK\b1\c&H393535&\bord0\fs40\frz270\pos(1863.369,777.612)}告日本国民书 请立即离开城市
Dialogue: 1,1:47:00.89,1:47:03.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正中等线_GBK\c&H393535&\bord0\fs40\frz270\pos(1578.788,803.766)}这张传单上写的事情十分重要\h\h\n请务必认真阅读。\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\n各位日本国民现在面临着一个\h\h\n十分严峻的秋天。军部高层的\h\h\n家伙已经无视了「十三条之宽\h\h\n大条款」给予日本停止无谓的\h\h\n战争的机会。\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h
Dialogue: 1,1:47:00.89,1:47:03.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正中等线_GBK\c&H393535&\bord0\fs40\frz270\pos(1540.259,746.674)}为此苏联已经对日本宣战。
Dialogue: 1,1:47:00.89,1:47:03.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正中等线_GBK\c&H393535&\bord0\fs40\frz270\pos(1337.198,818.887)}并且美国已经发明并使用了无论\h\h\n多少人都无法匹敌的原子弹。\h\h\h\n这种原子弹仅一个就能与两千架\h\h\n巨大的B-29轰炸机投下的炸弹\h\h\h\n匹敌\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.89,1:47:03.39,kono-text-cn - tips,,0,0,0,,注：十三条之宽大条款指的是「波茨坦公告」
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.89,1:47:03.39,kono-zs,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&HFFFFFF&\bord3\1a&H64&\an5\pos(1641.777,784.568)}m 0 0 l 0 500 l 650 500 l 650 0\N
Dialogue: 1,1:47:01.76,1:47:04.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,请让我一直待在这里
Dialogue: 1,1:47:06.54,1:47:08.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,老是让人担心
Dialogue: 1,1:47:08.38,1:47:09.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 1,1:47:09.99,1:47:12.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,笨蛋 笨蛋 笨蛋 笨…
Dialogue: 1,1:47:13.00,1:47:14.58,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 1,1:47:15.89,1:47:16.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 1,1:47:17.50,1:47:18.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,非常对不起
Dialogue: 1,1:47:20.18,1:47:21.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 1,1:47:21.59,1:47:23.42,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,一个都打不中
Dialogue: 1,1:47:23.69,1:47:26.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这样又要给海兵团的人欺负了
Dialogue: 1,1:47:27.32,1:47:28.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 1,1:47:28.68,1:47:31.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,捡到美军的传单不交上去的话
Dialogue: 1,1:47:31.29,1:47:33.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,又会被宪兵们斥责的
Dialogue: 1,1:47:34.21,1:47:36.57,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就算交上去也只是被烧了而已
Dialogue: 1,1:47:36.88,1:47:40.71,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,像这样做成厕纸还更加有用
Dialogue: 1,1:47:40.99,1:47:42.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 1,1:47:42.75,1:47:45.23,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不过暂时厕所就不能借给外人就是了
Dialogue: 1,1:47:45.63,1:47:49.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,用尽所有方法生存下去就是我的战斗了
Dialogue: 1,1:47:52.20,1:47:53.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 1,1:47:53.38,1:47:54.42,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 1,1:47:54.83,1:47:58.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,死于战阵 殉于职守
Dialogue: 1,1:47:58.37,1:48:04.06,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,毙于非命者及其遗属
Dialogue: 1,1:48:04.24,1:48:06.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,则五脏为之俱裂
Dialogue: 1,1:48:06.01,1:48:10.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,至于负战伤 蒙战祸
Dialogue: 1,1:48:10.43,1:48:13.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,失家业者之生计
Dialogue: 1,1:48:13.78,1:48:17.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,忍所难忍 耐所难耐
Dialogue: 1,1:48:17.99,1:48:20.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,以为万世之太平
Dialogue: 1,1:48:20.26,1:48:25.53,kono-text-cn-2,,0,0,0,,天皇陛下的玉音已恭敬地播送完毕
Dialogue: 1,1:48:23.38,1:48:25.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,结束了结束了
Dialogue: 1,1:48:25.85,1:48:26.98,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这个是
Dialogue: 1,1:48:27.15,1:48:29.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就是输了的意思吗
Dialogue: 1,1:48:30.18,1:48:31.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 1,1:48:31.16,1:48:34.40,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,广岛和长崎都给投放了新型的炸弹
Dialogue: 1,1:48:34.41,1:48:38.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,苏联也参战了 打不过的
Dialogue: 1,1:48:39.21,1:48:41.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这不是都已经做好觉悟了吗
Dialogue: 1,1:48:42.15,1:48:45.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不是说要战斗到最后一个人吗
Dialogue: 1,1:48:45.47,1:48:47.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,现在这里就还有五个人
Dialogue: 1,1:48:47.98,1:48:51.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我还有左手 双脚还留着
Dialogue: 1,1:48:59.27,1:49:00.52,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,晴美
Dialogue: 1,1:49:01.46,1:49:03.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,晴美
Dialogue: 1,1:49:10.70,1:49:12.22,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,都飞走了
Dialogue: 1,1:49:12.47,1:49:13.98,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我至今为止的一切
Dialogue: 1,1:49:14.89,1:49:17.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我认为很好的东西
Dialogue: 1,1:49:17.85,1:49:20.86,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,所以一直忍耐着的理由
Dialogue: 1,1:49:23.33,1:49:27.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,从海的对面过来的大米 大豆
Dialogue: 1,1:49:27.01,1:49:30.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我们是用这些东西做成的吗
Dialogue: 1,1:49:31.52,1:49:34.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,所以我们就得屈服于暴力吗
Dialogue: 1,1:49:37.69,1:49:42.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真想什么都不去考虑 就在迷糊中死去
Dialogue: 1,1:49:55.32,1:50:00.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这是万一到了最后的时候 给大家存着的
Dialogue: 1,1:50:01.53,1:50:04.14,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,今天就什么都不加地煮吧
Dialogue: 1,1:50:04.60,1:50:06.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不能全部煮掉就是了
Dialogue: 1,1:50:06.38,1:50:10.07,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,还有明天和后天呢
Dialogue: 1,1:50:15.87,1:50:22.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,8月15日 16日 17日
Dialogue: 1,1:50:24.43,1:50:27.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,9月 10月
Dialogue: 1,1:50:28.43,1:50:30.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,11月和下一年
Dialogue: 1,1:50:31.63,1:50:34.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,再下一年 10年后也
Dialogue: 1,1:50:35.61,1:50:37.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,一直 一直
Dialogue: 1,1:50:49.16,1:50:51.42,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,白得闪闪发亮呢
Dialogue: 1,1:50:51.75,1:50:53.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不过没有什么配菜
Dialogue: 1,1:50:53.85,1:50:54.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 1,1:50:55.33,1:50:56.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,周作呢
Dialogue: 1,1:50:56.61,1:50:57.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,还没回来
Dialogue: 1,1:50:57.89,1:51:02.17,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,事已至此 作为法务部的工作就更应该守护好秩序吗
Dialogue: 1,1:51:02.98,1:51:04.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我们先开动吧
Dialogue: 1,1:51:06.89,1:51:09.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,再也没炸弹落下 所以也没有浮上来的鱼了
Dialogue: 1,1:51:10.07,1:51:11.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那个时候
Dialogue: 1,1:51:23.49,1:51:25.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你在做什么呢
Dialogue: 1,1:51:25.29,1:51:27.56,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,难得的白米饭都看不见了
Dialogue: 1,1:51:40.40,1:51:42.14,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,终于上陆了
Dialogue: 1,1:51:42.79,1:51:44.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我要调动到大竹去
Dialogue: 1,1:51:45.32,1:51:47.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,到海军解体为止
Dialogue: 1,1:51:47.52,1:51:51.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,无论发生什么 都要守护好秩序就是法务部的工作
Dialogue: 1,1:51:53.74,1:51:56.47,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这种时候 要是有双手的话
Dialogue: 1,1:51:56.56,1:52:01.06,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就能轻轻地握住他不安的手了
Dialogue: 1,1:52:02.82,1:52:04.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真是安静呢
Dialogue: 1,1:52:04.04,1:52:05.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,大家都准备好了
Dialogue: 1,1:52:06.29,1:52:08.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不好意思了 到这里就行了
Dialogue: 1,1:52:10.35,1:52:12.19,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,早点回家去吧
Dialogue: 1,1:52:13.19,1:52:14.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 1,1:52:17.22,1:52:19.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我绝对会回来的
Dialogue: 1,1:52:19.56,1:52:20.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,回到铃的身边
Dialogue: 1,1:52:22.20,1:52:22.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:52:24.05,1:52:27.51,kono-hmz,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正粗圆_gbk\frz291.8\pos(1324,404)\c&H9A9FA4&\fad(1022,0)}明天的米饭配给延期了
Dialogue: 1,1:52:25.36,1:52:28.65,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,盐和酱油一直都没有
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.05,1:52:33.01,kono-hmz,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1523,681)\fs50\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(347.022,221.155)}1945
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.05,1:52:33.01,kono-hmz,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1523,681)\fs70\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(349.466,290.91)}年
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.05,1:52:33.01,kono-hmz,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1523,681)\fs60\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(343.693,363.289)}11
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.05,1:52:33.01,kono-hmz,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1523,681)\fs70\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(348.396,431.739)}月
Dialogue: 1,1:52:34.08,1:52:35.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 姐姐
Dialogue: 1,1:52:35.39,1:52:36.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 铃
Dialogue: 1,1:52:36.65,1:52:38.53,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这是什么的队伍
Dialogue: 1,1:52:38.64,1:52:40.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不知道 什么都行
Dialogue: 1,1:52:40.99,1:52:43.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,反正什么都缺
Dialogue: 1,1:52:43.67,1:52:44.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嘛 说的也是
Dialogue: 1,1:52:46.23,1:52:49.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不过这座镇子也变了呢
Dialogue: 1,1:52:49.77,1:52:51.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,give me
Dialogue: 1,1:52:51.16,1:52:53.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,久夫现在也在模仿着那种事吗
Dialogue: 1,1:52:54.87,1:52:56.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,晴美也会做吗
Dialogue: 1,1:52:56.26,1:53:00.07,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是占领军的剩菜杂煮
Dialogue: 1,1:53:02.52,1:53:03.84,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,还有纸屑
Dialogue: 1,1:53:15.01,1:53:17.11,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 1,1:53:19.74,1:53:22.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这边就完全没有味道
Dialogue: 1,1:53:23.59,1:53:26.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然后我跟美国人指路后
Dialogue: 1,1:53:26.90,1:53:28.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就给了我巧克力
Dialogue: 1,1:53:28.69,1:53:32.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你也剪着这个发型 应该是把你当小孩子了吧
Dialogue: 1,1:53:38.16,1:53:39.59,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 1,1:53:39.71,1:53:41.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,拿那么多洋服去换
Dialogue: 1,1:53:42.46,1:53:43.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,没事哦
Dialogue: 1,1:53:44.51,1:53:45.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你不知道吧
Dialogue: 1,1:53:46.42,1:53:49.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,死在邻保馆旁的士兵
Dialogue: 1,1:53:49.13,1:53:51.12,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好像是我的孩子
Dialogue: 1,1:53:52.23,1:53:54.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,自己的孩子我都没能认出来
Dialogue: 1,1:53:56.80,1:53:59.22,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在你面前晴美也
Dialogue: 1,1:54:00.57,1:54:01.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,1:54:02.10,1:54:03.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 1,1:54:07.10,1:54:07.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 1,1:54:10.14,1:54:10.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 1,1:54:12.10,1:54:13.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,想念我的话
Dialogue: 1,1:54:14.58,1:54:16.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就笑吧
Dialogue: 1,1:54:18.59,1:54:22.76,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在这个世界普通地 认真地居住下去吧
Dialogue: 1,1:54:24.02,1:54:24.76,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 1,1:54:25.35,1:54:26.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,晴美
Dialogue: 1,1:54:26.91,1:54:29.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我看见那里有什么船了 晴美
Dialogue: 1,1:54:31.03,1:54:33.64,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在那里的是 青叶
Dialogue: 1,1:54:35.95,1:54:36.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哲
Dialogue: 1,1:54:37.71,1:54:40.14,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,现在在你笑容的尽头
Dialogue: 1,1:54:40.71,1:54:46.56,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,寄宿着跳动着兔子的大海 飞翔着鹭鸶的天空
Dialogue: 1,1:54:51.10,1:54:53.14,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,晴美笑的很开心
Dialogue: 1,1:54:53.28,1:54:56.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我也要笑着想起晴美的事
Dialogue: 1,1:54:57.17,1:55:01.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这之后 我要一直当笑容的化身
Dialogue: 1,1:55:01.59,1:55:05.17,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是呀 一直哭就太浪费了
Dialogue: 1,1:55:05.86,1:55:07.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,浪费盐分
Dialogue: 1,1:55:09.14,1:55:12.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真是多亏了海里的盐分呢
Dialogue: 1,1:55:12.58,1:55:15.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,婆婆 婆婆 千鹤子
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.88,1:55:17.89,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1523,681)\fs50\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5\pos(1570.442,184.327)}1946
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.88,1:55:17.89,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1523,681)\fs70\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5\pos(1544.062,222.057)}年
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.88,1:55:17.89,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1523,681)\fs60\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5\pos(1574.112,323.45)}1
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.88,1:55:17.89,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1523,681)\fs70\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5\pos(1543.686,365.083)}月
Dialogue: 1,1:55:17.36,1:55:18.43,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 1,1:55:20.84,1:55:21.84,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,澄
Dialogue: 1,1:55:23.08,1:55:24.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 1,1:55:24.49,1:55:26.23,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你剪头发了呢
Dialogue: 1,1:55:26.46,1:55:28.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,没事没事 不用起来
Dialogue: 1,1:55:28.44,1:55:29.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,身体不舒服吗
Dialogue: 1,1:55:30.18,1:55:32.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,稍微有点头晕而已
Dialogue: 1,1:55:33.19,1:55:35.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哎 真是懊悔啊姐姐
Dialogue: 1,1:55:35.90,1:55:39.98,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在这寒冷的天空没法帮忙海苔的工作
Dialogue: 1,1:55:42.25,1:55:45.22,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你不好好睡也不行
Dialogue: 1,1:55:49.60,1:55:55.51,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要是手还在就能画鬼哥哥的南洋冒险记了
Dialogue: 1,1:55:55.84,1:55:57.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那是怎样的
Dialogue: 1,1:55:57.22,1:55:58.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什么样的故事
Dialogue: 1,1:55:59.05,1:56:02.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鬼哥哥的运输船遇难
Dialogue: 1,1:56:03.51,1:56:07.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在南边的岛上用椰子叶做了个家
Dialogue: 1,1:56:07.93,1:56:09.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,满脸胡须
Dialogue: 1,1:56:10.17,1:56:12.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,娶了鳄鱼做老婆
Dialogue: 1,1:56:12.19,1:56:14.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鳄鱼是老婆吗
Dialogue: 1,1:56:15.92,1:56:18.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,会不会回来江波呢 鬼哥哥
Dialogue: 1,1:56:19.22,1:56:20.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,妈妈也…
Dialogue: 1,1:56:22.14,1:56:27.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那个早上 妈妈要做祭典的准备就去了趟镇子
Dialogue: 1,1:56:28.61,1:56:31.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,虽然爸爸和我到处找过了
Dialogue: 1,1:56:31.48,1:56:33.19,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,也没能找到
Dialogue: 1,1:56:33.86,1:56:37.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,爸爸十月就倒下了 马上就死去了
Dialogue: 1,1:56:38.15,1:56:40.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,连同学校一起火化了
Dialogue: 1,1:56:41.20,1:56:43.96,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,没时间通知你真是抱歉
Dialogue: 1,1:56:45.75,1:56:48.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,没能早点回来对不起
Dialogue: 1,1:56:48.95,1:56:50.92,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你没早点回来太好了
Dialogue: 1,1:56:51.82,1:56:54.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃 我变成这样了
Dialogue: 1,1:56:55.52,1:56:57.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我 能治好吗
Dialogue: 1,1:56:57.87,1:56:58.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,能治好的
Dialogue: 1,1:56:59.03,1:57:00.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,治不好就太奇怪了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,----插曲----
Dialogue: 1,1:57:03.52,1:57:09.13,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}明明叫做冬天
Dialogue: 1,1:57:09.50,1:57:18.76,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}却吹起了温暖的风
Dialogue: 1,1:57:21.38,1:57:33.65,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}时而带来大海的味道
Dialogue: 1,1:57:42.10,1:57:48.26,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}路上的碎片
Dialogue: 1,1:57:48.26,1:57:52.46,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}在一闪一闪地笑着
Dialogue: 1,1:57:53.42,1:58:03.30,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}太阳的手掌轻抚着你的后背
Dialogue: 1,1:58:16.73,1:58:22.61,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}海苔的幽暗将你怀抱
Dialogue: 1,1:58:39.40,1:58:45.34,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}再也听不到麻雀间的谈话
Dialogue: 1,1:58:49.67,1:58:55.52,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}也无法沐浴蒲公英的绒毛
Dialogue: 1,1:58:55.95,1:59:02.69,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}到达不了云缝形成的向阳处
Dialogue: 1,1:59:02.69,1:59:12.87,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}无法知晓身旁入梦人的梦境
Dialogue: 1,1:59:14.91,1:59:23.92,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}也无法踏入每天走过的道路
Dialogue: 1,1:59:27.87,1:59:30.93,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}以越来越快的速度
Dialogue: 1,1:59:30.93,1:59:34.06,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}变成了记忆
Dialogue: 1,1:59:34.22,1:59:40.90,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}那些闪闪发亮的日子
Dialogue: 1,1:59:43.27,1:59:45.40,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}而你
Dialogue: 1,1:59:45.87,1:59:53.49,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}却无能为力
Dialogue: 1,1:59:54.96,2:00:00.54,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}你不过是这个世界的
Dialogue: 1,2:00:00.54,2:00:05.03,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}一小部分而已
Dialogue: 1,2:00:05.93,2:00:10.92,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}是怀念你的
Dialogue: 1,2:00:10.92,2:00:18.00,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}零零碎碎的人和物
Dialogue: 1,2:00:23.78,2:00:29.80,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}拼凑集结起来的而已
Dialogue: 1,2:00:32.22,2:00:33.33,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}所以
Dialogue: 1,2:00:33.33,2:00:34.74,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}无论何时
Dialogue: 1,2:00:34.99,2:00:37.81,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}都准备着
Dialogue: 1,2:00:37.88,2:00:42.42,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}你的容身之所
Dialogue: 1,2:00:49.08,2:00:54.30,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}无论何处都寄宿着爱
Dialogue: 1,2:00:54.30,2:00:59.81,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}无论何处都寄宿着爱
Dialogue: 1,2:01:00.29,2:01:05.48,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}在不断变换着的这个世界
Dialogue: 1,2:01:05.86,2:01:11.57,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}到处寄宿着
Dialogue: 1,2:01:14.67,2:01:20.09,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}零零散散的爱
Dialogue: 1,2:01:24.92,2:01:27.57,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}你看
Dialogue: 1,2:01:27.62,2:01:30.77,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}现在那里也
Dialogue: 1,2:01:31.08,2:01:33.35,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}变成了你的
Dialogue: 1,2:01:33.35,2:01:38.22,kono-chaqu-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\blur5}一部分
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,----插曲----
Dialogue: 1,1:57:08.38,1:57:09.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,幸子
Dialogue: 1,1:57:10.60,1:57:11.33,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 1,1:57:14.76,1:57:17.52,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,清子 你是清子对吧
Dialogue: 1,1:57:19.46,1:57:23.40,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这个镇子大家都在找寻着不见了的某人
Dialogue: 1,1:57:23.99,1:57:28.21,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我也有两三次找到了玲的错觉
Dialogue: 1,1:57:29.91,1:57:30.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 1,1:57:34.17,1:57:35.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你平安回来了
Dialogue: 1,1:57:36.44,1:57:39.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,海军十一月也大部分解散了
Dialogue: 1,1:57:39.13,1:57:40.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不用工作了
Dialogue: 1,1:57:41.72,1:57:42.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 1,1:57:43.70,1:57:47.93,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我第一次遇见铃 就是在这桥上
Dialogue: 1,1:57:49.16,1:57:51.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不过已经回不到那个时候了
Dialogue: 1,1:57:51.91,1:57:55.45,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这座城镇和我们也会一直改变着吧
Dialogue: 1,1:57:55.67,1:57:57.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我无论何时都能认出铃
Dialogue: 1,1:57:58.44,1:58:01.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你这里有颗痣 马上就能认出来
Dialogue: 1,1:58:02.40,1:58:04.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,周作 谢谢你
Dialogue: 1,1:58:04.87,1:58:08.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在这世界的一隅找到我
Dialogue: 1,1:58:08.85,1:58:10.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,请不要离开我
Dialogue: 1,1:58:11.24,1:58:13.40,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,请一直陪在我身边
Dialogue: 1,1:59:25.67,1:59:27.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,没事没事没事
Dialogue: 1,1:59:27.28,1:59:30.94,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,总而言之 在广岛找到工作太好了
Dialogue: 1,1:59:30.94,1:59:31.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,1:59:35.03,1:59:38.30,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不过很远很麻烦呢
Dialogue: 1,1:59:38.30,1:59:39.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 1,1:59:43.89,1:59:47.58,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 没事哦 你吃吧
Dialogue: 1,1:59:47.83,1:59:51.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要不离开这边的家去那边生活吧
Dialogue: 1,1:59:51.86,1:59:54.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你还有妈妈和澄
Dialogue: 1,1:59:54.74,1:59:58.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不不 我从这边过去就好
Dialogue: 1,1:59:58.99,2:00:01.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,虽然也很担心广岛的事
Dialogue: 1,2:00:01.60,2:00:04.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不过吴是我选择的地方
Dialogue: 1,2:00:24.77,2:00:28.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,吴市 吴市
Dialogue: 1,2:00:28.38,2:00:29.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,吴市？
Dialogue: 1,2:00:29.87,2:00:32.17,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,对哦 这里是吴市
Dialogue: 1,2:00:32.64,2:00:35.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,被九座山峰守护着
Dialogue: 1,2:00:35.39,2:00:37.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,所以叫做「九岭」
Dialogue: 1,2:00:35.39,2:00:37.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1058.488,917.514)}吴市
Dialogue: 1,2:00:37.90,2:00:40.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,右边的是休山
Dialogue: 1,2:00:40.78,2:00:42.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,左边的是钵卷山
Dialogue: 1,2:00:44.15,2:00:47.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然后 正中间的是灰之峰
Dialogue: 1,2:00:50.91,2:00:53.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那个山麓 就是我们的家了
Dialogue: 1,2:01:03.00,2:01:04.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这个孩子
Dialogue: 1,2:01:06.27,2:01:08.53,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好多虱子啊
Dialogue: 1,2:01:09.17,2:01:13.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,烧锅开水 穿的东西也全都烫一遍
Dialogue: 1,2:01:13.41,2:01:15.47,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,总而言之先洗个澡吧
Dialogue: 1,2:01:15.47,2:01:18.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这个孩子最后洗好点吧
Dialogue: 1,2:01:18.24,2:01:19.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,总而言之先去浴室点火
Dialogue: 1,2:01:19.63,2:01:20.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,2:01:21.41,2:01:25.05,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,去年晴美的衣服 会不会有点小
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,----ed----
Dialogue: 1,2:01:59.41,2:02:04.12,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}鸟儿运来的种子
Dialogue: 1,2:02:04.23,2:02:08.59,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}在静悄悄地呼吸着
Dialogue: 1,2:02:09.23,2:02:13.51,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}它会带来什么样的景色呢
Dialogue: 1,2:02:13.51,2:02:19.72,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}在这土地中想象下吧
Dialogue: 1,2:02:27.51,2:02:31.79,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}悄悄地偷看下吧
Dialogue: 1,2:02:32.44,2:02:36.82,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}虽然有点可怕
Dialogue: 1,2:02:37.20,2:02:41.54,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不过我想看到充满阳光的世界
Dialogue: 1,2:02:41.62,2:02:47.88,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}这份心情是不会动摇的
Dialogue: 1,2:02:51.38,2:02:59.93,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}风的音色改变了的话
Dialogue: 1,2:03:01.28,2:03:11.73,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}雨的荆棘不见了的话
Dialogue: 1,2:03:30.03,2:03:34.38,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}这个世界在你的眼里
Dialogue: 1,2:03:34.59,2:03:39.26,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}看起来是什么样的呢
Dialogue: 1,2:03:39.45,2:03:44.06,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我在这里生根发芽
Dialogue: 1,2:03:44.23,2:03:49.01,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}在梦中的叹息
Dialogue: 1,2:03:49.02,2:04:05.04,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}将我的绒毛
Dialogue: 1,2:04:05.16,2:04:09.92,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}吹向远方
Dialogue: 1,2:04:31.26,2:04:35.03,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}无法实现的愿望
Dialogue: 1,2:04:36.19,2:04:39.86,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}传达不到的思念
Dialogue: 1,2:04:40.68,2:04:45.29,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}变成深深的颜色
Dialogue: 1,2:04:45.33,2:04:52.25,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}悄悄地将我浸染
Dialogue: 1,2:04:54.23,2:04:58.01,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}越过那个屋顶
Dialogue: 1,2:04:59.06,2:05:02.55,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}到旁边的城镇
Dialogue: 1,2:05:03.93,2:05:12.81,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}在不知何人的院子里
Dialogue: 1,2:05:13.81,2:05:17.19,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不知多少在地上
Dialogue: 1,2:05:18.65,2:05:22.28,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不知多少在船上
Dialogue: 1,2:05:23.51,2:05:33.71,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}只要到达了你的肩膀
Dialogue: 1,2:05:50.72,2:05:55.08,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}小小的火苗就会燃烧
Dialogue: 1,2:05:55.64,2:06:00.07,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}在土地上没有一丝声响
Dialogue: 1,2:06:00.57,2:06:04.87,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}明天自由之时到来的话
Dialogue: 1,2:06:04.90,2:06:12.46,kono-ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}便定能与你相见
